0expect%20that%20I'd%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20tiny%20home%20life%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20I'd%20use%20it%20as%20a%20way%20to%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20moving%20from%20Florida%20to%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETiny%20homes%20were%20a%20mystery%20to%20me%2C%20so%20I%20jumped%20into%20learning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itssimplyplaced.com%2Fpractical-minimalism-when-less-is-more%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epractical%20minimalist%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20tries%20to%20keep%20only%20what%20is%20necessary%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20tiny%20home%20was%20appealing%20to%20me%2C%20but%20there%20was%20so%20much%20I%20didn't%20know.%20That's%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgotinyacademy.weebly.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoTinyAcademy%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20in%2C%20a%20course%20I%20found%20out%20about%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tinyhouse.com%2Fevent%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20tiny%20house%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20decided%20to%20take%20so%20I%20could%20best%20prepare%20myself%20for%20the%20lifestyle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20took%20the%20class%20in%202020%2C%20the%20cost%20was%20%24250%20for%20a%2012-week%20course%20over%20Zoom.%20I%20and%20four%20other%20%26quot%3Bstudents%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20us%20women%20%E2%80%94%20would%20meet%20for%20about%2090%20minutes%20a%20week.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thespruce.com%2Fwomen-in-tiny-home-movement-5221280%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%20are%20the%20leading%20buyers%20of%20tiny%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20because%20it's%20more%20financially%20viable%2C%20or%20they're%20transitioning%20into%20different%20stages%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20like%20becoming%20an%20empty%20nester%20(as%20I%20was)%20or