igcaption%3EThe%20living%20room%20of%20Murphy's%20tiny%20home.%20Murphy%20says%20she%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpractical%20minimalist%26quot%3B%20who%20tries%20to%20keep%20only%20what's%20necessary.%3Cp%3EStacey%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20leap%20into%20tiny%20home%20life%2C%20I%20began%20an%20exhaustive%20search%20for%20a%20builder.%20It%20took%20a%20few%20months%2C%20but%20the%20long%20process%20paid%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20all%20was%20said%20and%20done%2C%20my%20house%20cost%20about%20%24150%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20money%20I'd%20saved%20up%20from%20investing%20aggressively.%20The%20builder%20completed%20about%2060%25%20of%20the%20home%2C%20and%20I%20finished%20the%20final%2040%25%20using%20a%20general%20contractor%2C%20trade%20specialists%2C%20and%20my%20own%20customization%3A%20I%20bought%20home%20improvement%20materials%20and%20major%20appliances%20at%20Lowe's%3B%20flooring%20and%20butcher%20block%20from%20LL%20Flooring%3B%20lighting%2C%20wallpaper%2C%20and%20kitchen%20hardware%20at%20Wayfair%3B%20cabinet%20hardware%20and%20specialty%20decor%20on%20Etsy%2C%20and%20other%20miscellaneous%20items%20on%20Amazon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20live%20in%20Ramona%2C%20California%2C%20about%2045%20minutes%20from%20downtown%20San%20Diego%2C%20in%20what%20I%20call%20my%20%26quot%3Btiny%20mansion.%26quot%3B%20It's%20550%20square%20feet%20total%2C%20and%20I'm%20part%20of%20a%20tiny%20home%20community%20that%20has%20a%20mix%20of%20tiny%20homes%20on%20wheels%2C%20park%20models%2C%20and%20manufactured%20homes.%20I%20love%20the%20vibe%20here%2C%20and%20the%20nature%2C%20and%20the%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20the%20home%20makes%20me%20more%20financially%20and%20environmentally%20conscious%2C%20with%20a%20smaller%20footprint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom%20of%20Stacey's%20tiny%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65382ed60487ff031cad4db5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe%20designed%20and%20customized%20the%20interior%20of%20her%20tiny%20home%2C%20including%20the%20bathroom.%3Cp%3EStacey%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20I%20would've%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20living%20in%20California%20otherwise%3B%20this%20is%20an%20area%20with%20expensive%20real%20estate.%20I%20can%20now%20afford%20luxuries%20for%20my%20tiny%20home%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20like%20a%20metal%20roof%2C%20higher-end%20appliances%2C%20and%20a%20full-house%20water%20filtration%20system%20%E2%80%94%20that%20otherwise%20would%20be%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20shocked%20there%20are%20several%20things%20that%20are%20cheaper%20in%20California%20than%20Florida%20%E2%80%94%20groceries%20is%20one%20of%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20no%20regrets%20about%20my%20choice%20to%20build%20a%20tiny%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20might%20find%20the%20small%20size%20daunting%2C%20but%20I%20love%20it.%20I%20love%20being%20surrounded%20by%20only%20the%20things%20I%20love%20and%20nothing%20frivolous.%20I%20love%20the%20tiny%20home%20community%20and%20how%20everyone%20has%20a%20similar%20mindset.%20We%20have%20such%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20community%20and%20it's%20lovely%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20people%20who%20value%20the%20same%20things%20you%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it's%20not%20all%20rainbows%20and%20butterflies.%20I'm%20having%20a%20hard%20time%20with%20cell%20reception%20in%20my%20tiny%20mansion%2C%20but%20that%20will%20be%20worked%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20overall%2C%20tiny%20home%20life%20has%20really%20surpassed%20my%20expectations.%20It%20turns%20out%20people%20don't%20need%20as%20much%20space%20as%20they%20think%20they%20do%20%E2%80%94%20honestly%2C%20you'd%20be%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20my%20daughter%20is%20the%20one%20that%20got%20me%20interested%20in%20the%20tiny%20home%20lifestyle%2C%20she%20actually%20doesn't%20live%20in%20one%20yet.%20She%20might%20later%2C%20but%20it's%20me%20who%20really%20took%20the%20concept%20and%20ran%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-in-a-tiny-mansion-home-so-could-afford-california-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698312241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6538300d96f7540cd0649682%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-in-a-tiny-mansion-home-so-could-afford-california-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20moved%20into%20a%20tiny%20home%20mansion%20to%20afford%20living%20life%20in%20California.%20A%20tiny%20home%20on%20wheels%20allowed%20Stacey%20Murphy%2C%2055%2C%20to%20move%20to%20CA%20and%20afford%20more%20luxuries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Fortesa%20Latifi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-in-a-tiny-mansion-home-so-could-afford-california-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Goondagardi'%20Says%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20as%20ED%20Summons%20His%20Son%2C%20Raids%20Rajasthan%20Congress%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26144739%2FF9WlVtnaYAAHc5Y.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20has%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20led%20Union%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Egoondagardi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(hooliganism)%20after%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20Thursday%20issued%20summons%20to%20his%20son%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%20and%20conducted%20raids%20on%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Govind%20Singh%20Dostara.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%