Cp%3EOn%20October%2013%2C%20six%20days%20after%20Hamas'%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel%2C%20the%20technology%20conference's%20leader%2C%20Paddy%20Cosgrave%2C%20posted%20his%20views%20on%20the%20ensuing%20conflict%20on%20X.%20In%20his%20first%20post%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20Cosgrave%20seemed%20to%20accuse%20Israel%20of%20war%20crimes.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20shocked%20at%20the%20rhetoric%20and%20actions%20of%20so%20many%20Western%20leaders%20%26amp%3B%20governments%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20in%20particular%20of%20Ireland's%20government%2C%20who%20for%20once%20are%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpaddycosgrave%2Fstatus%2F1712790539844612553%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20he%20wrote%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWar%20crimes%20are%20war%20crimes%20even%20when%20committed%20by%20allies%2C%20and%20should%20be%20called%20out%20for%20what%20they%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20week%20of%20backlash%20that%20saw%20attendees%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintel-siemens-pull-out-cancel-sponsors-web-summit-ceo-israel-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emajor%20commercial%20partners%20including%20Intel%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20pulling%20out%20of%20Web%20Summit%2C%20due%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Lisbon%20in%20November%2C%20Cosgrave%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweb-summit-founder-paddy-cosgrave-apologized-for-remarks-on-israel-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eapologized%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20eventually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweb-summit-ceo-paddy-cosgrave-steps-down-over-israel-comments-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eresigned%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20saga%20mirrors%20flare-ups%20on%20US%20college%20campuses%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-harvard-columbia-law-students-lost-job-offers-israel-statements-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecompanies%20rescinding%20job%20offers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20students%20over%20student%20groups'%20statements%20on%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosgrave's%20departure%20illustrates%20the%20stakes%20for%20corporate%20executives%20when%20deciding%20whether%20or%20how%20to%20comment%20on%20any%20politically%20fraught%20subject.%20While%20students%20answer%20primarily%20to%20their%20school%20and%20any%20future%20employers%2C%20an%20executive's%20audience%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20include%20some%20combination%20of%20employees%2C%20shareholders%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20customers%2C%20often%20from%20multiple%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20whose%20views%20may%20differ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstand%20your%20audience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECosgrave%2C%20who%20is%20Irish%2C%20may%20not%20have%20accounted%20for%20a%20culture%20clash.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2023%2F10%2F09%2Fjoint-statement-on-israel%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOur%2520countries%2520will%2520support%2520Israel%2Cthese%2520attacks%2520to%2520seek%2520advantage.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20many%20European%20countries%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20count%20Israel%20as%20a%20staunch%20ally.%20Ireland's%20government%20has%20condemned%20Hamas'%20terrorist%20attacks%2C%20but%20it%20was%20reported%20on%20October%207%20that%20it%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irishtimes.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F10%2F07%2Fmicheal-martin-indicates-israeli-response-to-appalling-hamas-attack-has-not-been-proportionate%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMr%2520Martin%2520said%2520Israel%2520had%2Cthe%2520situation%2520at%2520this%2520stage.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emore%20explicitly%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20urged%20a%20%26quot%3Bproportionate%26quot%3B%20military%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIreland%20also%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20pro-Palestinian%20sentiment%2C%20much%20of%20it%20rooted%20in%20the%20country's%20relationship%20to%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20grassroots%20and%20the%20political%20elite%20are%20more%20pro-Palestinian%20than%20they%20are%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20Kissane%2C%20a%20politics%20professor%20at%20The%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%20and%20Political%20Science%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20for%20a%20number%20of%20factors.%20One%20is%20that%20historically%20the%20Irish%20regard%20themselves%20as%20having%20been%20a%20minority%20struggling%20against%20Britain%2C%20so%20they're%20more%20sympathetic%20to%20other%20anti-colonial%20or%20independent%20struggles%20%E2%80%94%20depending%20on%20what%20you%20regard%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIreland%20was%20the%20first%20Western%20nation%20to%20recognize%20the%20Palestinian%20Liberation%20Organization%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bsole%20legitimate%20representative%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%26quot%3B%20in%201980%2C%20and%20in%202021%20the%20Irish%20parliament%20accused%20Israel%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2021%2Fmay%2F26%2Fireland-israel-de-facto-annexation-palestinian-land%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIreland%2527s%2520parliament%2520has%2520voted%2Cexcoriated%2520Israel%2527s%2520treatment%2520of%2520Palestinians.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ede%20facto%20annexation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20of%20Palestinian%20land.%20Palestinian%20flags%20and%20murals%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irishnews.com%2Fnews%2Fnorthernirelandnews%2F2023%2F10%2F23%2Fnews%2Fireland_s_support_for_palestine_an_explainer-3720414%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efrequent%20republican%20neighborhoods%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Northern%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Web%20Summit%20began%20in%20Ireland%2C%20its%20audience%2C%20speakers%2C%20attendees%2C%20and%20commercial%20sponsors%20are%20now%20international.%20Current%20and%20former%20commercial%20sponsors%20include%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Siemens%2C%20per%20its%20website.%20And%20American%20CEOs%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Google's%20%E2%80%94%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-condemn-hamas-express-support-israel-messages-employees-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emostly%20explicitly%20condemned%20Hamas%20and%20expressed%20support%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosgrave%20possibly%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20really%20realize%20how%20big%20a%20deal%20it%20was%20given%20the%20diversity%20of%20his%20audience%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Argenti%2C%20a%20corporate%20communications%20professor%20at%20Tuck%20School%20of%20Business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Cosgrave's%20critics%2C%20including%20VCs%20and%20founders%2C%20his%20comments%20lacked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgdibner%2Fstatus%2F1713598569867878624%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bmoral%20clarity%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20failing%20to%20explicitly%20condemn%20Hamas%20in%20the%20first%20instance%2C%20while%20also%20suggesting%20the%20potential%20for%20Israeli%20war%20crimes.%20(Cosgrave%20later%20did%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpaddycosgrave%2Fstatus%2F1713879938229493838%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20condemn%20Hamas%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20But%20some%20of%20Cosgrave's%20Irish%20followers%2C%20including%20entrepreneurs%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcowenjones%2Fstatus%2F1715786502079135945%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacademics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20supported%20his%20remarks%20or%20took%20similar%20stances%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosgrave%20did%20not%20immediately%20reply%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20might%20have%20been%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20'You're%20absolutely%20right'%20in%20Ireland%2C%26quot%3B%20Argenti%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there's%20a%20push%20to%20be%20more%20pro-Israel%20in%20the%20US.%20No%20question%20about%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosgrave%20may%20have%20also%20erred%20in%20U-turning%2C%20itself%20indicative%20that%20he%20didn't%20fully%20think%20through%20the%20consequences%20of%20taking%20a%20public%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProceed%20with%20caution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20high-profile%20CEOs%20who%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-condemn-hamas-express-support-israel-messages-employees-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecommented%20on%20the%20conflict%20so%20far%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20explicitly%20condemned%20Hamas%20and%20supported%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20have%20yet%20to%20express%20an%20opinion%20may%20be%20mindful%20of%20previous%20blowback%20against%20corporate%20stances%20on%20topics%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbud-light-lost-beer-sales-crown-modelo-lgbtq-backlash-report-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELGBTQ%2B%20rights%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorge-floyd-protests-nike-facebook-real-corporate-leadership-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eracial%20justice%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArgenti%20said%20it%20was%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20companies%20are%20not%20political%20entities%20and%20that%20the%20expectation%20for%20them%20to%20comment%20on%20issues%20outside%20their%20core%20business%20is%20a%20relatively%20new%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEOs%20should%20consider%20whether%20commenting%20on%20a%20political%20topic%20issues%20is%20strategic%2C%20whether%20they%20can%20do%20anything%20practical%20to%20address%20the%20issues%2C%20and%20how%20much%20retaliation%20they%20might%20face%20either%20way%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20no%20connection%20to%20Israel%2C%20what%20is%20the%20point%20in%20mouthing%20off%20about%20political%20issues%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BDo%20we%20really%20want%20companies%20to%20become%20political%20entities%20is%20maybe%20an%20even%20better%20question.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20main%20advice%20for%20companies%20is%20to%20be%20really%20careful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BHave%20a%20plan%20for%20how%20you%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20issues%20before%20they%20come%20up%20%E2%80%94%20not%20when%20somebody's%20pressuring%20you%20to%20say%20something%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20stick%20to%20your%20guns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-israel-gaza-remarks-web-summit-paddy-cosgrave-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698311125000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652eba84211def8ed83754e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-israel-gaza-remarks-web-summit-paddy-cosgrave-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paddy%20Cosgrave's%20exit%20as%20Web%20Summit's%20CEO%20illustrates%20the%20thorny%20road%20for%20execs%20who%20might%20weigh%20in%20on%20the%20most%20sensitive%20topic%20in%20world%20news%20right%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-israel-gaza-remarks-web-summit-paddy-cosgrave-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ishaan%20Khatter%20on%20his%20bond%20with%20Shahid%20Kapoor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698311103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104723988%2Cimgsize-5