illegal%20activities%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20cronies%20are%20ruled%20licit%20by%20a%20corrupted%20legal%20system.%20Other%20hallmarks%20of%20a%20kleptocracy%20are%20rent-seeking%20through%20awarding%20lucrative%20contracts%20to%20family%20members%20or%20friends%20and%20reframing%20the%20domestic%20narrative%20by%20capturing%20ownership%20of%20media%20companies.%20Does%20this%20ring%20a%20bell%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FT%E2%80%99s%20investigative%20analysis%20is%20a%20damning%20indictment%20of%20the%20regime.%20It%20alleges%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20has%20been%20inflating%20imported%20coal%20costs%20by%20using%20offshore%20middlemen%2C%20because%20of%20which%20the%20price%20of%20coal%20more%20than%20doubles%20on%20landing%2C%20and%20thereby%2C%20the%20Indian%20consumer%20is%20being%20duped%20into%20paying%20twice%20his%20legitimate%20dues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20jaw-droppingly%20significant%20is%20that%20this%20regime%20knew%20what%20was%20going%20on%20and%20did%20nothing%20to%20stop%20the%20bleeding.%20Also%2C%20consumers%20may%20have%20paid%20for%20inflated%20coal%20prices%20between%202019%20and%202021%20when%20the%20pandemic%20had%20already%20hit%20their%20incomes%20and%20savings%20badly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20now%20one%20is%20not%20surprised%20at%20the%20unholy%20nexus%20between%20the%20corporates%20and%20this%20dispensation.%20The%20dubious%20Rafale%20deal%2C%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20dirt%2C%20the%20pricey%20airport%20and%20port%20contracts%2C%20et%20al%2C%20betray%20the%20lockstep%20between%20government%20and%20the%20most%20powerful%20business%20houses.%20More%20disturbing%20is%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20equivocal%2C%20if%20not%20complicit%2C%20stance%20on%20these%20critical%20matters%20of%20integrity%20and%20ethics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20not%20what%20the%20country%20bargained%20for%20when%20this%20regime%20first%20took%20up%20the%20reins%20almost%20a%20decade%20ago.%20In%202014%2C%20Modi%20rode%20to%20power%20on%20the%20back%20of%20an%20anti-corruption%20wave%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20messianic%20India%20Against%20Corruption%20(IAC)%20movement%20that%20organised%20a%20nationwide%20stir%20against%20endemic%20political%20and%20bureaucratic%20corruption%20and%20brought%20the%20jittery%2C%20dishonest%20UPA%20government%20down%20to%20its%20knees.%20In%20those%20heady%20days%20of%20fanciful%20idealism%2C%20we%20%E2%80%93%20the%20gullible%20fools%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20passionately%20believed%20that%20the%20potent%20Lokpal%20Act%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20accession%20would%20clean%20the%20Augean%20stables.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Strategy%20Lies%20in%20the%20Constant%20Use%20of%20Self-Image%20in%20the%20Religious%20Context%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-self-image-religion-politics-image%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Strategy%20Lies%20in%20the%20Constant%20Use%20of%20Self-Image%20in%20the%20Religious%20Context%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20towering%2C%20squeaky-clean%20persona%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20amplified%20by%20mobilising%20every%20possible%20propaganda%20tool%2C%20ensured%20that%20corruption%20as%20an%20issue%20of%20public%20concern%20dropped%20off%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20radar.%20His%20spurious%20public%20image%20of%20personal%20integrity%20for%20long%20subsumed%20criticism%20of%20corruption%20in%20his%20government.%20A%20credulous%20public%20was%20convinced%20that%20this%20superman%20had%20resolved%20the%20problem%20of%20corruption.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENa%20khaunga%20na%20khaane%20dhunga%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20beguiling%20catchphrase%20that%20calmed%20a%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpen%20democratic%20societies%20with%20free%20access%20to%20information%20are%20vital%20for%20fighting%20corruption.%20The%20most%20important%20outcome%20of%20transparency%20is%20that%20it%20has%20a%20civilising%20effect%20on%20political%20behaviour%20through%20democratic%20accountability.%20In%20fact%2C%20social%20thinkers%20contend%20that%20transparency%20and%20free%20flow%20of%20information%20contribute%20to%20regime%20effectiveness%20in%20matters%20ranging%20from%20development%20and%20growth%20to%20social%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20kleptocratic%20mode%20of%20governance%20can%20thrive%20only%20in%20an%20authoritarian%20and%20opaque%20milieu.%20This%20government%20has%20succeeded%20in%20creating%20an%20intimidatory%20environment%20of%20%E2%80%9Cshock%20and%20awe%E2%80%9D%20which%20has%20virtually%20terrorised%20every%20institution%20into%20toeing%20its%20line.%20A%20nameless%20fear%20has%20gripped%20government%20offices%20as%20the%20bureaucracy%20cowers%20behind%20the%20%E2%80%98steel%20frame%E2%80%99%20in%20an%20ecosystem%20where%20loyalty%20to%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20is%20paramount%20and%20not%20impartiality%20and%20probity.%20Nobody%20dares%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%20or%20challenge%20faulty%20government%20policies.%20This%20has%20had%20a%20terribly%20deleterious%20effect%20on%20the%20fight%20against%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20deadlier%20for%20the%20future%20because%20of%20its%20long-term%20impact%20has%20been%20the%20well%20thought%20out%2C%20methodical%20positioning%20of%20individuals%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cright%20ideological%20bent%E2%80%9D%20in%20critical%20government%20institutions%20including%20the%20UPSC%2C%20CAG%2C%20UGC%20and%20JNU.%20The%20sentinels%20of%20Hindutva%20have%20been%20planted%20everywhere.%20And%20those%2C%20like%20the%20intrepid%20professor%20K.S.%20James%2C%20director%20of%20the%20International%20Institute%20of%20Population%20Sciences%20(IIPS)%2C%20who%20refuse%20to%20bend%20but%20say%20it%20like%20it%20is%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-iips-director-resignation-nfhs-health-ministry%5C%22%3Eare%20booted%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20most%20institutions%20have%20become%20grovelling%20propagandists%20of%20the%20political%20executive.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20is%20what%20is%20expected%20of%20every%20public%20functionary%2C%20and%20the%20government%20makes%20no%20bones%20about%20it.%20Setting%20aside%20all%20principles%2C%20the%20government%20has%20decided%20that%20its%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%5C%22%3Ewill%20act%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Erath%20prabharis%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20spread%20information%20on%20the%20alleged%20achievements%20of%20the%20government.%20A%20similar%20diktat%20was%20earlier%20issued%20to%20the%20armed%20forces%20personnel%20proceeding%20on%20leave.%20Sycophancy%20is%20now%20an%20ordained%20public%20duty.%20Clearly%2C%20this%20government%20is%20bent%20on%20corrupting%20our%20souls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20oppressive%20environment%2C%20the%20institutions%20meant%20to%20combat%20corruption%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20mere%20ciphers.%20The%20calculated%20diminution%20of%20the%20Lokpal%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%20Although%20the%20Lokpal%20and%20Lokayuktas%20Act%20was%20enacted%20in%202013%2C%20this%20government%20with%20impunity%20deferred%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20the%20Lokpal%20by%20more%20than%20five%20years%20until%202019%2C%20in%20the%20meantime%20subverting%20the%20statute%20with%20critical%20amendments%20that%20diluted%20the%20powers%20and%20reach%20of%20the%20Lokpal.%20Predictably%2C%20only%20those%20well-disposed%20towards%20the%20government%20occupy%20the%20top%20posts%20in%20the%20supreme%20body%20ordained%20to%20fight%20corruption%20in%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20%E2%80%98Double%20Engine%E2%80%99%20is%20Pass%C3%A9%2C%20Hereafter%20Modi-Shah%20Will%20Pick%20or%20Junk%20BJP%20CMs%20at%20Will%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdouble-engine-bjp-modi-shah%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Double%20Engine%E2%80%99%20is%20Pass%C3%A9%2C%20Hereafter%20Modi-Shah%20Will%20Pick%20or%20Junk%20BJP%20CMs%20at%20Will%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20extant%20provisions%20in%20the%20Lokpal%20Act%20have%20been%20disregarded.%20The%20Act%20envisages%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20CBI%20to%20the%20Investigation%20and%20Prosecution%20wings%20of%20the%20Lokpal%2C%20but%20that%2C%20we%20know%20for%20sure%2C%20will%20not%20happen%20so%20long%20as%20Modi%20is%20around.%20Instead%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccaged%20parrot%E2%80%9D%20has%20transmuted%20into%20a%20deadly%20force%20that%20is%20being%20used%20to%20settle%20scores%20with%20the%20opponents%20of%20the%20regime.%20We%20have%20a%20Lokpal%20alright%2C%20but%20one%20that%20is%20innocuous%20and%20a%20pale%20shadow%20of%20the%20ombudsman%20that%20the%20people%20of%20India%20had%20rooted%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEqually%20worrying%20is%20the%20systematic%20undermining%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20law%20which%20is%20aimed%20at%20tearing%20down%20the%20wall%20of%20bureaucratic%20secrecy%20behind%20which%20governments%20do%20their%20dirty%20work.%20Fortified%20by%20this%20government%E2%80%99s%20imprimatur%20of%20opacity%20in%20governance%2C%20major%20public%20organisations%20are%20guilty%20of%20routinely%20withholding%20information%20on%20matters%20of%20public%20interest.%20By%20far%20the%20most%20infamous%20instance%20is%20the%20Delhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20comply%20with%20an%20RTI%20application%20seeking%20to%20verify%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20BA%20degree%20and%20despite%20the%20chief%20information%20commissioner%20directing%20the%20university%20to%20disclose%20the%20information.%20(Even%20more%20surreal%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20courts%20have%20upheld%20the%20non-disclosure%20of%20our%20leading%20public%20functionary%E2%80%99s%20academic%20credentials.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20entire%20media%20focus%20on%20the%20venality%20and%20depredations%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20other%20opponents%20of%20the%20regime%2C%20the%20everyday%2C%20all-pervasive%20corruption%20faced%20by%20the%20ordinary%20citizen%20is%20dismissed%20as%20a%20piffling%20problem%20that%20we%20are%20expected%20to%20take%20in%20our%20stride.%20According%20to%20the%20Global%20Corruption%20Barometer%20(GCB)%20compiled%20by%20Transparency%20International%20in%20November%202020%2C%20India%20has%20the%20dubious%20distinction%20of%20the%20highest%20bribery%20rate%20(39%25)%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20greatest%20number%20of%20people%20who%20use%20personal%20connections%20to%20access%20public%20services%20(46%25).%20Most%20respondents%20(89%25)%20felt%20that%20corruption%20in%20government%20is%20the%20main%20problem.%20A%20large%20number%20(63%25)%20think%20that%20reporting%20corruption%20would%20invite%20retaliation.%20India%20languishes%20at%2086th%20out%20of%20180%20countries%20in%20the%202022%20Corruption%20Perception%20Index%20with%20a%20score%20of%2040%20which%20is%20worse%20than%20the%20global%20average%20score%20of%2043.%20Clearly%2C%20%E2%80%9Cna%20khaunga%2C%20na%20khaane%20dhunga%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20cruel%20joke%20played%20on%20the%20people%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20see%20today%20is%20not%20only%20corruption%20by%20individuals%20but%20wholesale%2C%20across%20the%20board%20subornation%20of%20systems%20and%20institutions.%20At%20a%20metaphysical%20level%2C%20the%20frontal%20assault%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20secular%20India%20has%20corrupted%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20soul%20(a%20broken%20Manipur%20is%20the%20first%20casualty).%20And%20the%20greatest%20irony%20is%20that%2C%20perched%20atop%20the%20biggest%20scams%20in%20our%20history%20and%20a%20deeply%20unhappy%20and%20divided%20India%20of%20his%20making%2C%20the%20Vishwaguru%20still%20unabashedly%20claims%20to%20be%20leading%20the%20fight%20against%20corruption%2C%20repeatedly%20accusing%20the%20Opposition%20of%20fostering%20criminality%20and%20advising%20his%20puppets%20in%20the%20central%20probe%20agencies%20not%20to%20spare%20the%20corrupt.%20The%20hypocrisy%20is%20stunning!%20F.W.%20Robertson%20had%20people%20like%20the%20Vishwaguru%20in%20mind%20when%20he%20observed%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20three%20things%20in%20the%20world%20that%20deserves%20no%20mercy%20%E2%80%93%20hypocrisy%2C%20fraud%20and%20tyranny.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20The%20views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698310843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26142523%2FF8N0WYKXEAAQlm-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finarguably-the-most-corrupt-regime-ever%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20we%20see%20today%20is%20not%20only%20corruption%20by%20individuals%20but%20wholesale%2C%20across%20the%20board%20subornation%20of%20systems%20and%20institutions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finarguably-the-most-corrupt-regime-ever%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women%20who%20work%20in%20Utah's%20Silicon%20Slopes%20share%20its%20dark%20side%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20suit%20and%20a%20woman's%20face%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650a0a85bf943d00195bf4ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EiStock%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interview%20for%20an%20engineering%20job%20at%20a%20Utah%20tech%20company%2C%20Trina%20Limpert%20was%20told%20she%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Brisky%20hire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20she%20got%20the%20job%2C%20Limpert%20still%20feels%20frustrated%20remembering%20her%20first%20day.%20As%20a%20network%20engineer%2C%20she%20had%20to%20prove%20herself%20by%20showing%20she%20could%20put%20together%20computer%20hardware.%20The%20male%20hires%20were%20given%20no%20such%20test%20and%20instead%20received%20shiny%20new%20desktops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20got%20in%20and%20met%20everyone%20else%20I%20was%20working%20with%2C%20I%20was%20just%20as%20skilled.%20I%20was%20just%20as%20qualified%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Limpert%2C%20now%20the%20CEO%20of%20RizeNext%2C%20a%20Utah-based%20leadership-training%20consultancy%20she%20founded.%20She%20believes%20the%20only%20reason%20she%20was%20told%20she%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Brisky%20hire%26quot%3B%20was%20because%20she's%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20the%20only%20time%20she%20felt%20like%20she%20was%20being%20treated%20differently%20than%20male%20colleagues%20in%20Silicon%20Slopes%2C%20Utah's%20term%20for%20its%20tech%20industry.%20Limpert%20said%20she'd%20been%20passed%20over%20for%20promotions%20because%20people%20assumed%20a%20husband%20was%20providing%20for%20her%2C%20while%20she%20watched%20men%20get%20promotions%20because%20people%20assumed%20they%20were%20the%20primary%20breadwinners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSexism%20exists%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Limpert%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20an%20extra%20layer%20here.%20That's%20why%20I%20chose%20not%20to%20work%20at%20startups%20in%20Utah.%20Stereotypes%20of%20gender%20norms%20are%20extremely%20heavy%20here.%20There's%20the%20expectation%20you%20should%20be%20at%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUtah%20has%20a%20unique%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%20It%20is%20ranked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Fnews%2Fbest-states%2Frankings%2Feconomy%2Femployment%2Fjob-growth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighest%20in%20job%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20it's%20projected%20to%20be%20the%20top%20state%20for%20tech%20job%20growth%20for%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cyberstates.org%2Fpdf%2FCompTIA_State_of_the_tech_workforce_2023.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20from%20The%20Computing%20Technology%20Industry%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20are%20attracted%20to%20Utah%20because%20of%20its%20job%20opportunities%2C%20reasonable%20housing%20prices%2C%20abundant%20natural%20beauty%2C%20and%20its%20family-friendly%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20many%20other%20states%20with%20plentiful%20tech%20jobs%2C%20it%20ranks%20abysmally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwallethub.com%2Fedu%2Fbest-and-worst-states-for-women-equality%2F5835%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20on%20women's%20equality%20data%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20research%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech-worker%20transplants%20have%20moved%20to%20Utah%20only%20to%20be%20shocked%20by%20the%20culture%20there%2C%20multiple%20people%20said.%20Insider%20spoke%20to%2022%20women%20who%20previously%20or%20currently%20work%20at%20Utah%20tech%20companies%20told%20Insider.%20Some%20asked%20for%20anonymity%20so%20they%20could%20speak%20freely%20and%20to%20avoid%20retribution.%20Their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20all%20of%20these%20women%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20they%20experienced%20unequal%20treatment%20at%20their%20jobs%20or%20witnessed%20it%20for%20other%20women.%20Several%20women%20reported%20traumatic%20work%20experiences%20and%20shared%20personal%20stories%20about%20facing%20discrimination%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraditionally%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20very%20conservative%20state%2C%20where%20women's%20labor-force%20participation%20has%20been%20low%2C%26quot%3B%20Claudia%20Geist%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20sociology%20and%20gender%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Utah%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20the%20expectation%20that%20women%20are%20primary%20caregivers.%20Changing%20those%20ingrained%20perspectives%20is%20just%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFast-paced%20tech%20meets%20family-values%20conservatism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20true%20that%20statistics%20and%20individual%20experiences%20can%20never%20fully%20capture%20a%20culture%2C%20and%20many%20Utah%20tech%20companies%20are%20making%20efforts%20to%20hire%20and%20promote%20more%20women%2C%20as%20well%20as%20offer%20family-friendly%20benefits%20that%20benefit%20both%20men%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20true%20that%20women%20experience%20similar%20issues%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20the%20tech%20industry%20at%20large.%20Women%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20are%20far%20less%20likely%20to%20receive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffemale-founders-bias-diversity-legal-tech-lawyers-women-vc-funding-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eventure-capital%20funding%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20major%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-racism-sexism-mental-health-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincluding%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevery-company-that-was-sued-discrimination-and-harassment-lawsuits-2020-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUber%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-microsoft-women-idUSKCN1GP077%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-facebook-pay-gap-hire-more-women-ireland-uk-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20faced%20complaints%20or%20lawsuits%20from%20female%20employees%20alleging%20sexism%20and%20unequal%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Utah%2C%20these%20tech-industry%20tendencies%20can%20be%20more%20intense%2C%20according%20to%20the%20women%20who%20spoke%20to%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESilicon%20Slopes%2C%20named%20for%20Utah's%20world-class%20ski%20slopes%2C%20is%20headquarters%20for%20tech%20companies%20like%20Ancestry%2C%20Domo%2C%20Entrata%2C%20Pluralsight%2C%20Qualtrics%2C%20and%20hosts%20outposts%20for%20others%20like%20Adobe%20and%20a%20Meta%20data-center.%20It%20has%20a%20burgeoning%20startup%20community%20fueled%20by%20talent%20from%20Brigham%20Young%20University%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Utah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20states%20that%20are%20havens%20for%20tech%20jobs%2C%20such%20as%20California%2C%20Washington%2C%20and%20New%20York%2C%20Utah%20has%20a%20decidedly%20politically%20conservative%20bent%2C%20with%20four%20times%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvote.utah.gov%2Fcurrent-voter-registration-statistics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregistered%20Republican%20voters%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20registered%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUtah%20is%20also%20the%20home%20base%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.churchofjesuschrist.org%2Fstudy%2Fscriptures%2Fthe-family-a-proclamation-to-the-world%2Fthe-family-a-proclamation-to-the-world%3Flang%3Deng%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Church%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20of%20Latter-day%20Saints%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usu.edu%2Fuwlp%2Ffiles%2Fwp%2Fno-4.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%2060%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20state's%20population%20are%20members%20of%20the%20church.%20Mormons%2C%20who%20are%20heavily%20represented%20in%20Utah's%20tech%20scene%2C%20also%20tend%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Freligion%2F2009%2F07%2F24%2Fa-portrait-of-mormons-in-the-us-social-and-political-views%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elean%20conservative%20both%20socially%20and%20politically%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20influences%20the%20state's%20tech%20culture.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20church's%20Quorum%20of%20the%20Twelve%20Apostles%20spoke%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsummit.siliconslopes.com%2Fspeakers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20Silicon%20Slopes%20Summit%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20held%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20research%20reports%20have%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwallethub.com%2Fedu%2Fbest-and-worst-states-for-women-equality%2F5835%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20ranked%20the%20state%20poorly%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20areas%20of%20women's%20equality.%20Utah%20has%20the%20third%20worst%20gender%20pay%20gap%20among%20US%20states%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chamberofcommerce.org%2Fgender-pay-gap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20median%20income%20for%20men%20about%2037%25%20higher%20than%20it%20is%20for%20women.%20That's%20a%20slightly%20bigger%20gap%20than%20Washington%2C%20home%20to%20Seattle's%20tech%20hub%2C%20but%20significantly%20worse%20than%20California%20and%20New%20York%2C%20where%20the%20gap%20is%20about%2014%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjobs.utah.gov%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F2022%2F11%2F28%2Futah-s-gender-wage-gap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Community%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%209.2%25%20of%20women%20in%20Utah%20and%2013.5%25%20of%20men%20earn%20a%20college%20degree%20above%20a%20bachelor's%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usu.edu%2Fuwlp%2Ffiles%2Fwp%2Fno-4.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewider%20gap%20in%20educational%20attainment%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20in%20any%20other%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20Utah%20also%20tend%20to%20have%20larger%20families%2C%20with%2028%25%20of%20the%20population%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjobs.utah.gov%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F2022%2F11%2F28%2Futah-s-gender-wage-gap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunder%20the%20age%20of%2018%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Because%20women%20often%20shoulder%20more%20childcare%20duties%2C%20particularly%20in%20socially%20conservative%20societies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjobs.utah.gov%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F2022%2F11%2F28%2Futah-s-gender-wage-gap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E62%25%20of%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Utah%20with%20children%20under%206%20participate%20in%20the%20labor%20force%2C%20compared%20to%2072%25%20of%20US%20women%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20factors%20influence%20women's%20experiences%20in%20Silicon%20Slopes%2C%20keeping%20them%20from%20reaching%20leadership%20positions%20while%20contributing%20to%20difficult%20work%20experiences%2C%20the%20women%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUtah%20is%20not%20in%20a%20very%20strong%20position%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20women%20in%20business%20in%20general%2C%20whether%20you're%20more%20in%20the%20tech%20corporate%20sector%20or%20whether%20you%20are%20a%20woman%20in%20small%20business%20and%20entrepreneurship%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robyn%20Cohen%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20W%20Collective%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20supporting%20women%20in%20tech%20and%20venture%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20male-bonding%20boys'%20club%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Kuo%2C%20the%20head%20of%20talent%20acquisition%20at%20JumpSearch%2C%20said%20she%20experienced%20culture%20shock%20when%20she%20relocated%20to%20Silicon%20Slopes.%20Kuo%20previously%20lived%20in%20Southern%20California%2C%20where%20she%20worked%20with%20more%20women%20and%20people%20of%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20in%20general%20don't%20get%20as%20much%20opportunity%20to%20move%20up%20as%20often%20unless%20the%20company%20is%20open-minded%20and%20diverse%2C%26quot%3B%20Kuo%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20culturally%2C%20women%20tend%20to%20stay%20at%20home.%20They're%20basically%20raised%20to%20be%20a%20homemaker.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20women%20%E2%80%94%20both%20Mormon%20and%20not%20%E2%80%94%20described%20their%20Utah%20tech%20companies%20as%20a%20Mormon%20boys'%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20commonly%20recruit%20talent%20after%20they%20complete%20their%20two-year%20missions%20for%20the%20church.%20The%20experience%20of%20spreading%20the%20word%20about%20their%20faith%20is%20seen%20as%20valuable%20work%20experience%2C%20particularly%20for%20sales%20teams%2C%20some%20of%20the%20women%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20sell%20religion%2C%20you%20can%20sell%20anything.%20That's%20the%20joke%20around%20why%20there's%20so%20many%20sales%20teams%20based%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20woman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20teams%20are%20often%20dominated%20by%20men%20and%20%26quot%3Bmale%20bonding%26quot%3B%20outside%20work%20is%20common%2C%20which%20means%20fewer%20women%20participate%20in%20out-of-office%20conversations.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20a%20big%20boys'%20club%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20woman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20been%20warned%20for%20decades%20by%20church%20leaders%20not%20to%20be%20alone%20with%20women%20other%20than%20their%20wives%2C%20many%20Mormon%20men%20won't%20meet%20with%20women%20one-on-one%20for%20lunch%20or%20coffee%2C%20multiple%20women%20said.%20Such%20attitudes%20may%20be%20slowly%20changing%20but%20are%2C%20for%20some%2C%20still%20deeply%20ingrained%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sltrib.com%2Fnews%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2Fno-no-for-a-man-to-have-a-business-lunch-with-a-woman-not-his-spouse-such-thinking-may-be-rooted-in-past-mormon-counsel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20Tribune%20reported%20in%202017.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20feeling%20of%20discomfort%20among%20men%20and%20women%20working%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robbyn%20Scribner%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Tech-Moms%2C%20a%20group%20that%20helps%20women%20move%20into%20the%20tech%20industry.%20%26quot%3BThe%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-laughed-about-the-mike-pence-rule-and-said-his-vp-was-ahead-of-his-time-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Mike%20Pence%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20still%20alive%20and%20well.%20This%20comes%20back%20to%20the%20church.%20I%20am%20a%20member%20of%20the%20church%2C%20but%20I'm%20a%20feminist%20active%20member%20of%20my%20church.%20There's%20a%20long-standing%20policy%20that%20men%20and%20women%20should%20not%20be%20alone%20together%20if%20they're%20not%20married.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20described%20instances%20of%20not%20being%20invited%20to%20golf%20outings%2C%20volleyball%20games%2C%20or%20the%20gym%20during%20lunch.%20One%20woman%20said%20she%20was%20asked%20to%20surpass%20her%20sales%20quota%2C%20while%20men%20on%20her%20team%20hit%20the%20gym%20during%20lunch%20once%20they%20hit%20their%20quotas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20got%20the%20best%20territories%2C%20these%20had%20been%20guys%20who%20had%20weight-lifting%20buddies.%20There%20was%20this%20kind%20of%20sense%20that%20if%20you%20wanted%20to%20get%20ahead%2C%20you%20had%20to%20do%20weight%20lifting%20and%20hunting%20and%20boy%20stuff%20with%20the%20guys%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20woman%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20felt%20sort%20of%20left%20behind%20because%20I%20didn't%20do%20all%20that%20even%20though%20my%20performance%20was%20still%20really%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20salesperson%20said%20she%20started%20getting%20fewer%20sales%20leads%20and%20felt%20she%20was%20getting%20pushed%20out%20after%20her%20boss%20learned%20she%20was%20pregnant.%20She%20wanted%20to%20move%20to%20a%20different%20team%20but%20was%20offered%20entry-level%20pay%20for%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20so%20insulted%20by%20that%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20I'm%20out%20of%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20was%20a%20guy%2C%20they%20would%20have%20paid%20top%20dollar.%20They%20were%20just%20looking%20at%20me%20as%20a%20way%20to%20push%20me%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20cybersecurity%20analyst%20recounted%20how%20she%20had%20to%20advocate%20for%20maternity%20leave%20when%20she%20got%20pregnant%20at%20her%20previous%20Utah%20employer.%20She%20argued%20that%20three%20months%20of%20maternity%20leave%20was%20necessary%20and%20had%20to%20compare%20it%20to%20how%20a%20field%20worker%20would%20need%20time%20off%20to%20recover%20from%20knee%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can't%20imagine%20putting%20kids%20in%20day%20care%20let%20alone%20having%20a%20successful%20woman%20in%20the%20family%2C%20being%20a%20breadwinner%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there's%20not%20much%20legal%20help%20in%20the%20state%20for%20families%20seeking%20childcare%20help%20so%20both%20parents%20can%20work.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%202020%20bill%20that%20would%20provide%20tax%20breaks%20for%20employers%20offering%20childcare%20benefits%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deseret.com%2Futah%2F2020%2F2%2F21%2F21147234%2Futah-suzanne-harrison-child-care-industry-incentives-business-tax-breaks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20yet%20to%20gain%20traction%20in%20the%20state%20legislature%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLaws%20to%20promote%20more%20opportunities%20for%20women%20have%20been%20diminished%20because%20of%20that%20focus%20on%20how%20women%20should%20focus%20more%20on%20families%20rather%20than%20careers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scribner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20%26quot%3Bbenevolent%20sexism.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20common%20everywhere%2C%20but%20especially%20in%20more%20conservative%20and%20religious%20societies%20where%20there's%20more%20of%20a%20divide%20in%20gender%20roles%2C%20said%20Susan%20Madsen%2C%20a%20Utah%20State%20University%20business%20professor%20who%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usu.edu%2Fuwlp%2Ffiles%2Fwp%2Fno-4.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eled%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20women's%20equality%20in%20Utah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMen%20may%20make%20well-meaning%20comments%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20you%20take%20more%20time%20with%20your%20kids%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20go%20to%20this%20event%20this%20evening%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20which%20leaves%20women%20with%20fewer%20opportunities%20for%20advancement.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20subtle%20but%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20impact%20a%20woman's%20advancement%20and%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHR%20policy%3A%20Confront%20the%20boss%20who%20harasses%20you%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20women%20described%20experiences%20that%20crossed%20the%20line%20from%20sexism%20to%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20said%20she%20often%20got%20propositioned%20by%20married%20men%20who%20would%20invite%20her%20to%20hotels.%20Another%20said%20male%20colleagues%20would%20touch%20her%20without%20permission%2C%20putting%20their%20arms%20around%20her%20back%20or%20their%20hands%20on%20her%20waist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20a%20while%2C%20I%20learned%20there%20was%20somebody%20who%20got%20kicked%20out%20of%20the%20company%20because%20he%20did%20the%20same%20thing%20to%20another%20female%20employee%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20one%20of%20the%20men%20who%20had%20harassed%20her.%20She%20said%20she%20stayed%20%26quot%3Bquiet%20at%20the%20time%20because%20I%20was%20traumatized.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20handle%20it%20that%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20most%20of%20her%20colleagues%20were%20white%2C%20male%2C%20and%20Mormon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20wives%20are%20at%20home.%20In%20the%20engineering%20department%2C%20it's%20mostly%20all%20male%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20there's%20a%20female%2C%20it%20makes%20them%20a%20target%20for%20that%20because%20there's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20women%20they%20interact%20with%20daily.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20women%20who%20said%20they%20experienced%20sexual%20harassment%20came%20up%20against%20problems%20when%20they%20reported%20incidents.%20One%20woman%20said%20she%20reported%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20and%20the%20company's%20policy%20was%20that%20she%20had%20to%20confront%20her%20harasser%2C%20who%20was%20a%20higher-level%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20did%20confront%20him%20about%20it%2C%20she%20received%20no%20follow-up%20from%20her%20company%20until%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20later.%20She%20had%20to%20re-explain%20to%20HR%20what%20happened%20and%20send%20proof%20of%20her%20previous%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20her%20harasser%20had%20gotten%20promoted%20and%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20harassing%20someone%20else%2C%20she%20said.%20He%20was%20finally%20let%20go%20more%20than%20two%20years%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20stayed%20with%20the%20company%20because%20I%20did%20want%20to%20make%20it%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20really%20frustrating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20things%20are%20changing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Richards%2C%20a%20managing%20partner%20at%20Startup%20Ignition%20Ventures%2C%20moved%20to%20Utah%20from%20Seattle%2020%20years%20ago.%20He%20said%20the%20difference%20between%20when%20he%20arrived%20and%20now%20is%20like%20%26quot%3Bnight%20and%20day.%26quot%3B%20Today%2C%20more%20women%20are%20working%20in%20tech%2C%20and%20men's%20attitudes%20toward%20women%20have%20evolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Utah's%20tech%20industry%20still%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%2C%20including%20in%20closing%20the%20pay%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Richards%20said%20his%20firm%20works%20to%20recruit%20women%20for%20its%20entrepreneurship%20boot%20camp%2C%20women%20in%20Utah%20often%20leave%20the%20workforce%20to%20stay%20home%20to%20raise%20children.%20And%20those%20who%20don't%20stay%20home%20are%20still%20doing%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20domestic%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20fair%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20women%20who%20still%20do%20most%20of%20the%20domestic%20chores%20at%20home%20even%20if%20they're%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20Richards%20said.%20%26quot%3BWorking%20at%20a%20tech%20company%20in%20a%20high-pressure%20job%2C%20and%20then%20you%20also%20gotta%20go%20home%20and%20carry%20a%20huge%20burden%20of%20domestic%20responsibilities.%20That's%20all%20changing%2C%20but%20it's%20changing%20gradually.%20Women%20are%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there%20are%20some%20women%20working%20in%20Silicon%20Slopes%20who%20do%20view%20their%20companies%20as%20equitable%20workplaces%20and%20see%20positive%20role%20models%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I'm%20pretty%20fortunate%2C%26quot%3B%20Emily%20Perkins%2C%20a%20content%20research%20manager%20for%20Ancestry%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20work%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20women%2C%20and%20I%20do%20have%20a%20manager%20that's%20a%20woman%20and%20a%20CEO%20that's%20a%20woman%20and%20a%20vice%20president%20of%20our%20company%20that%20is%20a%20woman.%20I%20feel%20pretty%20lucky%20in%20that%20regard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAncestry%2C%20one%20of%20Utah's%20most%20established%20tech%20companies%2C%20hired%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ancestry.com%2Fcorporate%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fdeborah-liu-named-chief-executive-officer-ancestry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20executive%20Deborah%20Liu%20as%20CEO%20in%202021.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiu%2C%20known%20for%20championing%20diversity%20in%20technology%2C%20is%20the%20cocreator%20of%20the%20Women%20in%20Product%20nonprofit.%20Ancestry's%20chief%20product%20officer%20is%20Heather%20Friedland%2C%20who%20previously%20worked%20at%20Glassdoor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAncestry%20says%20that%2038%25%20of%20its%20leadership%20roles%20are%20held%20by%20people%20from%20diverse%20communities%2C%20which%20includes%20women%2C%20people%20of%20color%2C%20LGBTQ%2B%20people%2C%20veterans%2C%20and%20people%20with%20disabilities.%20The%20company%20didn't%20break%20out%20statistics%20on%20women%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ancestry.com%2Fcorporate%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fancestry-releases-%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20its%20first%20diversity%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20released%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20proud%20of%20the%20female%20tech%20leadership%20at%20Ancestry%2C%20but%20we%20know%20there%20is%20still%20more%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashlee%20Davis%2C%20Ancestry's%20global%20head%20of%20DEI%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20committed%20to%20fostering%20an%20inclusive%20workforce%20that%20is%20reflective%20of%20our%20diverse%20world%2C%20and%20we're%20proud%20to%20partner%20with%20other%20Utah%20companies%20that%20share%20that%20commitment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20change%20may%20happen%20for%20Silicon%20Slopes%20because%20the%20lack%20of%20female%20representation%20is%20having%20a%20measurable%20impact.%20Limpert%20said%20she's%20gotten%20calls%20from%20executives%20at%20Utah%20companies%20hoping%20to%20go%20public%20who've%20told%20her%20that%20NASDAQ%20won't%20work%20with%20them%20because%20their%20leadership%20is%20made%20up%20entirely%20of%20white%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20labor%20market%20in%20Utah%20is%20extremely%20tight%2C%26quot%3B%20Scribner%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20import%20a%20lot%20of%20talent%20from%20other%20states.%20A%20lot%20of%20women%20getting%20recruited%20from%20other%20areas%2C%20other%20states%2C%20look%20at%20a%20company%20that's%20all%20white%2C%20Mormon%20men%2C%20and%20say%2C%20'I%20don't%20want%20to%20move%20my%20life%20and%20my%20family.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20state%20looks%20to%20recruit%20more%20tech%20workers%2C%20there's%20a%20growing%20awareness%20that%20damaging%20attitudes%20toward%20female%20talent%20must%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20we're%20the%20worst%20state%20for%20women's%2