%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fairtel-logs-1-7-mn-unique-5g-customers-in-northeast-covers-110-districts-123102600500_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fairtel-logs-1-7-mn-unique-5g-customers-in-northeast-covers-110-districts-123102600500_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20Make%20Decisions...%26quot%3B%3A%20Pakistan%20Board%20On%20Babar%20Azam's%20Captaincy%20Future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20on%20Thursday%20hinted%20that%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam's%20captaincy%20could%20be%20on%20the%20line%20if%20the%20team's%20campaign%20in%20the%20ongoing%20World%20Cup%20fails.%20Pakistan%20are%20in%20a%20must-win%20situation%20against%20a%20marauding%20South%20Africa%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Friday%20and%20a%20loss%20will%20virtually%20end%20their%20hopes%20of%20progressing%20to%20the%20semifinals%2C%20as%20they%20have%20suffered%20three%20consecutive%20defeats%20in%20five%20matches%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAddressing%20the%20media%20scrutiny%20directed%20at%20captain%20Babar%20Azam%20and%20the%20team%20management%2C%20the%20board's%20stance%2C%20echoing%20that%20of%20former%20cricketers%2C%20is%20that%20successes%20and%20defeats%20are%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20Captain%20Babar%20Azam%20and%20Chief%20Selector%20Inzamam-ul-Haq%20were%20given%20freedom%20and%20support%20in%20forming%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PCB%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20ahead%2C%20the%20board%20will%20make%20decisions%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20Pakistan%20cricket%20based%20on%20the%20team's%20performances%20in%20the%20World%20Cup.%20At%20present%2C%20the%20PCB%20encourages%20fans%2C%20former%20players%20and%20stakeholders%20to%20rally%20behind%20the%20team%20as%20they%20strive%20to%20make%20a%20triumphant%20comeback%20in%20the%20mega-event.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistan%20have%20four%20points%20from%20five%20matches%2C%20having%20suffered%20consecutive%20defeats%20against%20arch-rivals%20India%2C%20Australia%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalls%20have%20grown%20for%20Babar%20to%20be%20removed%20from%2050-over%20captaincy%20following%20the%20shocking%20eight-wicket%20loss%20to%20Afghanistan%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20if%20Pakistan%20can%20stage%20a%20miracle%20and%20win%20all%20their%20remaining%20matches%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20semifinals%20of%20this%20World%20Cup%20does%20Babar%20stand%20any%20chance%20of%20surviving%20as%20captain%20and%20even%20then%20he%20might%20be%20relegated%20to%20skipper%20in%20just%20the%20red-ball%20format%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20reliable%20source%20close%20to%20the%20developments%20had%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20Ahmed%2C%20Muhammad%20Rizwan%20and%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20are%20reportedly%20being%20discussed%20as%20potential%20candidates%20who%20could%20replace%20Babar%20as%20captain%20when%20the%20national%20team%20returns%20home%20from%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistan%20are%20scheduled%20to%20tour%20Australia%20immediately%20after%20the%20World%20Cup.%20The%20team%20also%20needs%20to%20plan%20for%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20and%202025%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20clear%20consensus%20developing%20in%20the%20PCB%20that%20Babar%20has%20had%20his%20chance%20to%20prove%20himself%20and%20he%20has%20failed%20to%20deliver%20as%20captain%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPCB%20said%20it%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20fans%20at%20home%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20continue%20supporting%20the%20skipper%20during%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PCB%20acknowledges%20the%20emotions%20and%20sentiments%20of%20cricket%20fans%20following%20the%20three%20c