th%20of%20the%20Israeli%20city%20of%20Ashkelon%20but%20could%20not%20verify%20when%20the%20footage%20was%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20appeared%20to%20show%20an%20airstrike%20and%20later%20buildings%20being%20struck%20with%20munitions%2C%20sending%20debris%20flying%20high%20into%20the%20air%2C%20along%20with%20a%20thick%20plume%20of%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20hours%20earlier%20Netanyahu%20had%20delivered%20a%20nationally%20televised%20address%20to%20Israelis%20still%20grieving%20and%20furious%20after%20Hamas's%20bloody%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20telling%20them%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20campaign%20for%20our%20existence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shock%20attack%20saw%20throngs%20of%20Hamas%20gunmen%20pour%20from%20Gaza%20into%20Israel%2C%20killing%201%2C400%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20kidnapping%20222%20more%2C%20according%20to%20official%20tallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20retaliated%20with%20heavy%20bombing%20that%20Gaza's%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20said%20has%20killed%20more%20than%206%2C500%2C%20with%20the%20toll%20expected%20to%20rise%20substantially%20if%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Israeli%20troops%20massed%20near%20Gaza%20move%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Raining%20down%20hellfire'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20ever-louder%20international%20calls%20to%20temper%20the%20ferocious%20bombing%20campaign%2C%20vowed%20to%20press%20ahead%20with%20plans%20for%20a%20ground%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoasting%20of%20%26quot%3Braining%20down%20hellfire%20on%20Hamas%26quot%3B%20and%20killing%20%26quot%3Bthousands%20of%20terrorists%26quot%3B%2C%20Netanyahu%20said%20his%20war%20cabinet%20and%20the%20military%20would%20determine%20the%20timing%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bground%20offensive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20pledged%20to%20%26quot%3Beliminate%20Hamas%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbring%20our%20captives%20home%26quot%3B%20but%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20detail%20when%2C%20how%20or%20how%20many%26quot%3B%20forces%20would%20take%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20raid%20into%20Gaza%20was%20not%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20military%20told%20AFP.%20But%20it%20was%20likely%20to%20raise%20tensions%20in%20an%20already%20anxious%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20is%20among%20the%20foreign%20leaders%20stepping%20up%20public%20calls%20for%20Israel%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20innocent%20civilians%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20follow%20the%20%26quot%3Blaws%20of%20war%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20pursues%20Hamas%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20he%20had%20privately%20suggested%20Israel%20should%20get%20hostages%20out%20if%20possible%20before%20any%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20their%20decision%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20demand%20it%26quot%3B%2C%20Biden%20said%2C%20as%20he%20called%20on%20Congress%20to%20allocate%20more%20money%20for%20Israeli%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Cairo%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20warned%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20massive%20intervention%20that%20would%20put%20civilian%20lives%20at%20risk%20would%20be%20an%20error.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'It's%20a%20massacre'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza's%20Hamas-controlled%20health%20ministry%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20death%20toll%20had%20surged%20by%20about%20700%20in%20a%20day%20to%20above%206%2C500%2C%20including%20many%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Biden%20has%20stated%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20confidence%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Hamas%20ministry%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20death%20toll%20may%20be%20unclear%2C%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20suffering%20is%20not%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEntire%20neighbourhoods%20have%20been%20razed%2C%20surgeons%20in%20hospitals%20overwhelmed%20with%20wounded%20carry%20out%20procedures%20without%20anaesthetic%2C%20and%20ice%20cream%20trucks%20have%20become%20makeshift%20morgues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20waging%20war%20on%20Hamas%2C%20they're%20waging%20war%20on%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20charged%20one%20resident%2C%20Abu%20Ali%20Zaarab%2C%20after%20his%20family%20home%20was%20bombed%20in%20the%20southern%20town%20of%20Rafah.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20massacre.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%201.4%20million%20people%20--%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Gaza's%20population%20--%20have%20been%20displaced%2C%20according%20to%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20says%2012%20of%20the%20territory's%2035%20hospitals%20have%20closed%20due%20to%20damage%20or%20insufficient%20fuel%2C%20and%20a%20key%20UN%20aid%20agency%20serving%20almost%20600%2C000%20Palestinians%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bbegan%20to%20significantly%20reduce%20its%20operations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20cut%20off%20Gaza's%20normal%20supply%20corridors%20for%20water%2C%20food%20and%20other%20necessities%2C%20and%20fewer%20than%2070%20relief%20trucks%20have%20entered%20the%20impoverished%20territory%20since%20the%20war%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENone%20contained%20fuel%2C%20which%20Israel%20fears%20Hamas%20will%20use%20for%20rockets%20and%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAid%20agencies%20have%20warned%20that%20more%20people%20will%20die%20if%20medical%20equipment%2C%20water%20desalination%20plants%20and%20ambulances%20stop%20operating%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20generators%20stop%2C%20hospitals%20will%20%26quot%3Bturn%20into%20morgues%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Red%20Cross%20has%20warned.%20Hospitals%20are%20also%20struggling%20with%20a%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20and%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20performed%20a%20number%20of%20surgeries%20without%20anaesthetic%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ahmad%20Abdul%20Hadi%2C%20an%20orthopaedic%20surgeon%20working%20at%20Nasser%20hospital%20in%20Khan%20Yunis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20tough%20and%20painful%2C%20but%20with%20the%20lack%20of%20resources%2C%20what%20can%20we%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20regional%20'explosion'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20sparked%20fears%20of%20a%20regional%20conflagration%20if%20it%20draws%20in%20more%20of%20Israel's%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20October%207%2C%20Israel%20has%20launched%20thousands%20of%20strikes%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20hit%20targets%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELate%20Wednesday%2C%20Lebanon-based%20Hezbollah%20fired%20what%20Israel%20said%20was%20a%20surface-to-air%20missile%20at%20an%20Israeli%20drone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20it%20had%20intercepted%20the%20missile%20and%20%26quot%3Bstruck%20the%20source%20of%20the%20launch%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20Hezbollah%20and%20Syria's%20government%20are%20backed%20by%20Iran%2C%20which%20denies%20Israel's%20right%20to%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETehran's%20top%20diplomat%20on%20Wednesday%20accused%20Israel%20of%20carrying%20out%20%26quot%3Bgenocide%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJordan's%20King%20Abdullah%20became%20the%20latest%20leader%20to%20warn%20that%20ongoing%20violence%20could%20%26quot%3Blead%20to%20an%20explosion%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%20Queen%20Rania%20accused%20Western%20leaders%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bglaring%20double%20standard%26quot%3B%20for%20not%20condemning%20Israel's%20killing%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%20in%20its%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EViolence%20has%20also%20risen%20sharply%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20where%20health%20officials%20said%20more%20than%20100%20Palestinians%20had%20been%20killed%2C%20mostly%20in%20raids%20by%20Israeli%20troops%20or%20in%20clashes%20with%20Israeli%20settlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20