20the%20scourge%20of%20horrifying%20gun%20violence%20once%20again%20ripped%20through%20an%20American%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaine%20public%20safety%20official%20Mike%20Sauschuck%20said%20he%20was%20not%20prepared%20to%20give%20a%20death%20toll%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20fluid%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20reporters%20police%20were%20flooding%20the%20streets%20as%20they%20sought%20the%20gunman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20literally%20hundreds%20of%20police%20officers%20working%20around%20the%20state%20of%20Maine%20to%20investigate%20this%20case%2C%20to%20locate%20Mr.%20Card%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERescue%20vehicles%20rushed%20in%20from%20around%20central%20Maine%20to%20tend%20to%20the%20wounded%2C%20city%20councilor%20McCarthy%20said%2C%20and%20the%20two%20Lewiston%20hospitals%20%26quot%3Bhave%20called%20in%20every%20off-duty%20staff%20member%20that%20they%20could%20to%20deal%20with%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20made%20calls%20--%20stepping%20away%20from%20a%20state%20dinner%20honoring%20Australia's%20prime%20minister%20--%20to%20Maine's%20governor%2C%20its%20two%20senators%20and%20a%20local%20congressman%20to%20offer%20federal%20support%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%20Thursday%2C%20armed%20police%20were%20seen%20guarding%20the%20Central%20Maine%20Medical%20Center%2C%20where%20some%20of%20the%20wounded%20were%20being%20treated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Maine%20school%20boards%20and%20educational%20institutions%2C%20including%20Bates%20College%2C%20said%20they%20would%20not%20be%20holding%20classes%20on%20Thursday%2C%20according%20to%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMultiple%20locations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20and%20rescuers%20reportedly%20arrived%20at%20the%20Sparetime%20Recreation%20bowling%20alley%20at%20about%207%3A15%20pm%20local%20time%20(00%3A15%20Thursday%20GMT)%20in%20response%20to%20an%20active%20shooter%2C%20and%20then%20received%20reports%20of%20another%20shooting%20at%20the%20Schemengees%20Bar%20%26amp%3B%20Grille%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Sun%20Journal%20local%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20issued%20a%20number%20of%20photographs%20of%2040-year-old%20Card%20at%20the%20bowling%20alley%2C%20where%20he%20appears%20calm%20and%20composed%20as%20he%20moves%20through%20the%20doorway%20with%20his%20rifle%20raised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20contact%20law%20enforcement%20if%20you%20are%20aware%20of%20his%20whereabouts%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESauschuck%20said%20officers%20had%20located%20a%20%26quot%3Bvehicle%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20they%20had%20been%20looking%20for%20--%20a%20white%20sport%20utility%20vehicle%20(SUV)%20--%20in%20Lisbon%2C%20a%20town%20around%20eight%20miles%20(12%20kilometers)%20from%20Lewiston%2C%20where%20residents%20had%20also%20been%20warned%20to%20stay%20off%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECard%20was%20not%20in%20the%20vehicle%2C%20reports%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaw%20enforcement%20%26quot%3Bare%20investigating%20two%20active%20shooter%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Androscoggin%20County%20Sheriff's%20Department%20said%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20encouraging%20all%20businesses%20to%20lock%20down%20and%20or%20close%20while%20we%20investigate.%20The%20suspect%20is%20still%20at%20large.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaine%20Governor%20Janet%20Mills%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Baware%20of%20and%20have%20been%20briefed%20on%20the%20active%20shooter%20situation%20in%20Lewiston.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECNN%20reported%20that%20at%20least%2050%20people%20were%20wounded%20in%20the%20incidents%2C%20citing%20multiple%20law%20enforcement%20sources%2C%20but%20said%20it%20was%20unclear%20how%20many%20of%20the%20injuries%20were%20the%20result%20of%20gunfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20unclear%20if%20initial%20reports%20of%20shots%20being%20fired%20at%20a%20third%20site%2C%20a%20Walmart%20distribution%20center%2C%20were%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'My%20hometown'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaine%20Congressman%20Jared%20Golden%20wrote%20on%20social%20media%20that%20%26quot%3Blike%20all%20Mainers%2C%20I'm%20horrified%20by%20the%20events%20in%20Lewison%20tonight.%20This%20is%20my%20hometown.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20all%20of%20us%20are%20looking%20to%20local%20law%20enforcement%20as%20they%20gain%20control%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20gather%20information.%20Our%20hearts%20break%20for%20those%20who%20are%20affected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDistraught%20citizens%20flocked%20to%20local%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20overwhelmed.%20I've%20been%20here%20trying%20to%20spread%2C%20you%20know%2C%20some%20kind%20of%20comfort%2C%20some%20kind%20of%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20Cynthia%20Hunter%2C%20a%20local%20resident%2C%20told%20CBS%20affiliate%20WGME.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20is%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20since%202017%2C%20when%20a%20gunman%20opened%20fire%20on%20a%20crowded%20music%20festival%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20killing%20about%2060%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGun%20violence%20is%20alarmingly%20common%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20a%20country%20where%20there%20are%20more%20guns%20than%20people%20and%20where%20attempts%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20their%20spread%20are%20always%20met%20with%20stiff%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20recorded%20over%20500%20mass%20shootings%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Gun%20Violence%20Archive%20(GVA)%2C%20a%20non-governmental%20organization%20that%20defines%20a%20mass%20shooting%20as%20four%20or%20more%20people%20wounded%20or%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWednesday's%20attack%20was%20the%20deadliest%20mass%20shooting%20in%202023%20so%20far%2C%20according%20to%20the%20GVA's%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20