34.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Israel%20Kills%20Thousands%20of%20Palestinian%20Civilians%2C%20We%20Need%20to%20Pay%20Attention%20to%20the%20Language%20of%20'War'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20useful%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20lexicon%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20ongoing%20bloodbath%20in%20Palestine.%20Words%20which%20describe%20the%20murder%20of%20innocent%20civilians%20tells%20us%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20the%20Western%20world%20perceives%20the%20brutal%20and%20bloody%20colonisation%20of%20a%20nation%20and%20its%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETerms%20like%20war%2C%20conflict%20and%20killings%20could%20just%20as%20easily%20and%20accurately%20be%20replaced%20by%20genocide%2C%20annihilation%20and%20murder.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20language%20and%20narrative%20are%20always%20decided%20by%20the%20coloniser.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20media%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAJEnglish%2Fstatus%2F1716896359662428410%3Ft%3DFAdm2RIDNzwsFMUueEJ-TA%26s%3D08%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20other%20tools%20of%20narrative%20building%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20made%20it%20even%20easier%20for%20the%20powerful%20to%20%E2%80%98establish%E2%80%99%20truth%20and%20facts.%20To%20lie%20till%20it%20sounds%20like%20a%20resounding%20truth%20is%20what%20many%20political%20leaders%20have%20successfully%20learned%20to%20do%20across%20the%20globe.%20They%20use%20it%20as%20a%20means%20to%20gain%20power%20through%20the%20ballot%20box%20and%20worse%2C%20to%20murder.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20language%20and%20narrative%20built%20around%20the%20ongoing%20bombing%20of%20the%2025%20mile%20long%20strip%20of%20land%20which%20the%20children%20of%20Gaza%20believe%20is%20their%20home%20and%20homeland%2C%20is%20a%20classic%20example%20of%20this.%20This%20is%20how%20war%2C%20despite%20its%20ugliness%20and%20needlessness%2C%20becomes%20justified.%20Language%20thus%20becomes%20violence.%20Dead%20bodies%20served%20up%20as%20casualties%20of%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%20are%20always%20more%20acceptable%20than%20corpses%20dug%20out%20from%20mass%20graves%20of%20genocide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-palestine-israel-health-benjamin-netanyahu%5C%22%3EGaza%E2%80%99s%20Health%20System%20Had%20Already%20Been%20Weakened%20%E2%88%92%20the%20Siege%20Pushed%20it%20into%20Crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20coverage%20of%20the%20Gaza%20genocide%20by%20the%20Western%20and%20Indian%20media%20reeks%20of%20this%20violence%20of%20language.%C2%A0%20The%20brutal%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207%20in%20which%20hundreds%20of%20Israeli%20civilians%20were%20killed%20has%20become%20the%20pretext%20for%20whataboutery.%20The%20proponents%20of%20this%20whataboutery%20believe%20that%20all%20those%20being%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20at%20the%20moment%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20Israeli%20civilians%20and%20thus%20are%20liable%20for%20collective%20and%20cumulative%20punishment.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20the%20ordinary%20people%20of%20Gaza%20are%20being%20made%20to%20own%20a%20sin%20they%20did%20not%20commit.%20Just%20read%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnorthern-gaza-israel-palestine-conflict%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20the%20president%20of%20Israel%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20are%20no%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20justification%20is%20the%20language%20of%20violence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20western%20world%20very%20well%20recognises%20the%20impact%20of%20language%20and%20the%20sheer%20violence%20it%20can%20unleash.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20call%20the%20current%20bombing%20and%20brutality%20in%20Gaza%20a%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20Palestine%20and%20Israel%20is%20to%20trivialise%20the%20injustices%20of%20the%20Israeli%20regime.%20It%20dilutes%20the%20indisputable%20fact%20that%20Israel%20is%20illegally%20and%20violently%20in%20occupation%20of%20Palestinian%20territory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19124105%2Fgazarimal_2023-10-18_195802-1024x392.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19124105%2Fgazarimal_2023-10-18_195802-1024x392.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19124105%2Fgazarimal_2023-10-18_195802-300x115.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19124105%2Fgazarimal_2023-10-18_195802.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680776%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDestruction%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Photo%3A%20UNICEF%2FHassan%20Islyeh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Nazi%20minister%20for%20propaganda%20and%20public%20enlightenment%2C%20Joseph%20Goebbels%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPropaganda%20is%20absolutely%20necessary%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20only%20a%20means%20to%20an%20end.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20idea%20could%20never%20take%20over%20the%20state.%20I%20must%20be%20able%20to%20get%20what%20I%20think%20is%20important%20across%20many%20people.%E2%80%9D%20In%20other%20words%2C%20no%20narrative%20is%20useful%20till%20it%20is%20accepted%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20population.%20It%20does%20not%20astonish%20me%20anymore%20that%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20the%20Indian%C2%A0%20media%20and%20social%20media%20universe%20continues%20to%20participate%20whole%20heartedly%20in%20the%20buildup%20and%20sustenance%20of%20the%20Israeli%20narrative%20surrounding%20this%20crisis.%20There%20are%20the%20same%20people%20who%20support%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20regime%20in%20India.%20They%20see%20India%E2%80%99s%20stand%20in%20favour%20of%20Palestine%20in%20the%20past%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20previous%20regimes%20to%20%E2%80%98appease%E2%80%99%20Indian%20Muslims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPernicious%20hatred%20for%20Muslims%20is%20the%20glue%20which%20binds%20them%20with%20the%20Israeli%20narrative.%20They%20fail%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20problem%20is%20not%20an%20exclusively%20Muslim-Jew%20issue.%20India%E2%80%99s%20historic%20support%20to%20Palestine%20was%20based%20on%20our%20commitment%20and%20continuum%20of%20the%20anti-colonial%20legacy%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20It%20was%20no%20more%20an%20attempt%20at%20%E2%80%98appeasement%E2%80%99%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%20than%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20stand%20against%20apartheid%20in%20South%20Africa%20or%20its%20support%20for%20the%20national%20liberation%20struggles%20of%20other%20colonised%20people%20in%20Africa%20and%20Asia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20official%20Israeli%20narrative%20is%20costing%20human%20lives%20in%20thousands.%20The%20Israeli%20state%20is%20out%20there%20avenging%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20with%20a%20brutality%20and%20force%20unknown%20even%20to%20its%20tormented%20victims.%20They%20believe%20they%20are%20bringing%20the%20culprits%20to%20%E2%80%98justice%E2%80%99%20without%20realising%20that%20the%20line%20between%20justice%20and%20revenge%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20precariously%20thin.%20It%20is%20so%20thin%20that%20it%20becomes%20non-existent%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20careless.%20Revenge%20is%20the%20tool%20of%20the%20weak%20and%20the%20angry.%20Justice%20is%20never%20delivered%20in%20anger.%20It%20weighs%20evidence%20and%20situations%20in%20context%20of%20the%20crime.%20The%20evidence%20has%20always%20been%20against%20Israel%2C%20right%20from%20its%20wrongful%20inception%20in%201948.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20loss%20of%20a%20moral%20compass%20can%20plunge%20societies%20into%20a%20free%20fall%20of%20madness%20and%20brutality.%20Building%20up%20narratives%20that%20contribute%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20children%2C%20women%20and%20the%20elderly%20is%20murder%20with%20malice.%20Frantz%20Fanon%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C..because%20quite%20simply%20it%20was%2C%20in%20more%20than%20one%20way%2C%20becoming%20impossible%20for%20them%20%5Bthe%20colonised%5D%20to%20breathe%E2%80%9D.%20Palestinians%20need%20to%20breathe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShah%20Alam%20Khan%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Orthopaedics%2C%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698306405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fas-israel-kills-thousands-of-palestinian-civilians-we-need-to-pay-attention-to-the-language-of-war%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Building%20up%20narratives%20that%20contribute%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20children%2C%20women%20and%20the%20elderly%20is%20murder%20with%20malice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fas-israel-kills-thousands-of-palestinian-civilians-we-need-to-pay-attention-to-the-language-of-war%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAatank%20Macha%20Rakha%20Hai...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20After%