0to%20happen%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20online%20product%20delivery.%20More%20often%20than%20not%2C%20people%20end%20up%20receiving%20different%20items%20instead%20of%20the%20things%20they%20ordered.%C2%A0In%20a%20similar%20instance%2C%20a%20man%20claimed%20that%20he%20received%20a%20Thomson%20TV%20instead%20of%20the%20Sony%20TV%20he%20ordered%2C%20which%20was%20worth%20Rs%201%20lakh.%C2%A0The%20user%20named%20Aryan%20shared%20his%20ordeal%20on%20X%2C%20where%20it%C2%A0gained%20widespread%20attention.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20he%20was%20eagerly%20waiting%20for%20Flipkart's%20Big%20Billion%20Days%20sale%20to%20buy%20a%20Sony%20TV%20so%20that%20he%20could%20enjoy%20the%20ongoing%20ICC%20Men's%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20on%20a%20big%20screen.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20left%20shocked%20when%20the%20TV%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20low-priced%20one%20from%20another%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20thread%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20''I%20had%20purchased%20a%20Sony%20tv%20from%C2%A0%40Flipkart%C2%A0on%207th%20Oct%2C%20delivered%20on%2010th%20Oct%20and%20sony%20installation%20guy%20came%20on%2011th%20Oct%2C%20he%20unboxed%20the%20tv%20himself%20and%20we%20were%20shocked%20to%20see%20a%20Thomson%20tv%20Inside%20Sony%20box%20too%20with%20no%20accessories%20like%20stand%2C%20remote%2C%20etc.''%C2%A0He%20also%20shared%20pictures%20of%20the%20unboxing%2C%20stating%20that%20he%20immediately%20connected%20with%20Flipkart's%20customer%20care%20and%20raised%20the%20issue%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20get%20resolved%20even%20after%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20post%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20had%20purchased%20a%20Sony%20tv%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFlipkart%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Flipkart%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%207th%20oct%2C%20delivered%20on%2010th%20oct%20and%20sony%20installation%20guy%20came%20on%2011th%20oct%2C%20he%20unboxed%20the%20tv%20himself%20and%20we%20were%20shocked%20to%20see%20a%20Thomson%20tv%20Inside%20Sony%20box%20that%20too%20with%20no%20accessories%20like%20stand%2Cremote%20etc%201%2Fn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FiICutwj1n0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FiICutwj1n0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Aryan%20(%40thetrueindian)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthetrueindian%2Fstatus%2F1717015251043090511%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E''I%20raised%20this%20issue%20instantly%20with%20Flipkart%20customer%20care%20and%20they%20asked%20me%20to%20upload%20images%20of%20the%20tv%2C%20I%20have%20uploaded%20images%20as%20instructed%2C%20still%2C%20they%20asked%20me%20two%20or%20three%20times%20to%20upload%20images%20and%20I%20have%20uploaded%20as%20asked%2C''%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20after%20uploading%20the%20images%20multiple%20times%20as%20requested%2C%20the%20company%20hasn't%20processed%20his%20return%20request.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''Firstly%20they%20gave%20me%20a%20resolution%20date%20of%20the%2024th%20oct%20but%20on%20the%2020th%20they%20first%20showed%20it%20as%20resolved%20and%20then%20extended%20the%20date%20to%20the%201st%20of%20Nov.%20Today%20also%20they%20showed%20me%20that%20the%20issue%20is%20resolved%20but%20even%20my%20return%20request%20has%20not%20been%20processed.%C2%A0I%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20BBD%20to%20buy%20a%20TV%20so%20I%20can%20watch%20the%20World%20Cup%20on%20a%20good%20big%20screen%20but%20this%20service%20from%20FK%20has%20pushed%20me%20into%20stress%20which%20is%20really%20unbearable.%20Plz%20help%2C''%20he%20wrote%20further.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFlipkart%20responded%20to%20the%20man's%20viral%20post%20saying%2C%20''Our%20deepest%20apologies%20for%20your%20experience%20with%20the%20return%20request.%20We%20want%20to%20sort%20this%20out%20for%20you.%20P