t%20card%20interchange%20fees.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Matthew%20-%20PA%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%20and%20Bruce%20Bennett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUS%20airlines%20are%20banding%20together%20to%20criticize%20the%20Credit%20Card%20Competition%20Act%20of%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20say%20it%20will%20cut%20revenues%20of%20major%20payment%20networks%2C%20making%20them%20pull%20out%20of%20rewards%20programs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bill%2C%20proposed%20in%20June%2C%20seeks%20to%20lower%20credit%20card%20transaction%20fees%20from%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20airlines%20are%20attacking%20a%20new%20bill%20in%20Congress%20that%20seeks%20to%20lower%20credit%20card%20swipe%20fees%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20effectively%20end%20most%20flyer%20miles%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2F118%2Fbills%2Fs1838%2FBILLS-118s1838is.xml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECredit%20Card%20Competition%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20introduced%20by%20Sen.%20Dick%20Durbin%20of%20Illinois%20in%20June%2C%20would%20compel%20big%20US%20banks%20to%20let%20businesses%20use%20at%20least%20one%20payment%20network%20that%20isn't%20Visa%20or%20Mastercard%20for%20credit%20card%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDurbin%20is%20taking%20aim%20at%20what%20he%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3BVisa-Mastercard%20duopoly%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20they%20control%20over%2080%25%20of%20credit%20card%20transactions%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20dominance%20in%20the%20market%20allows%20them%20to%20charge%20transaction%20fees%20of%20around%203%25%20for%20credit%20card%20payments%20%E2%80%94%20a%20cost%20that%20businesses%20usually%20pass%20on%20to%20their%20customers%20through%20higher%20prices%2C%20Durbin%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntroducing%20market%20competition%20for%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20would%20force%20them%20to%20lower%20their%20fees%2C%20and%20in%20turn%20lower%20prices%20for%20consumers%2C%20according%20to%20Durbin's%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20airlines%20have%20come%20out%20in%20force%20against%20the%20bill%2C%20saying%20that%20cutting%20revenues%20from%20payment%20networks%20like%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20would%20make%20these%20platforms%20far%20less%20willing%20to%20offer%20rewards%20programs%20like%20flyer%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20cards%20could%20no%20longer%20receive%20the%20funding%20to%20be%20able%20to%20invest%20in%20rewards-back%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%20CEO%20Ed%20Bastian%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-10-24%2Fmajor-airline-ceos-predict-loyalty-program-doom-under-proposal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20we're%20watching%2C%20obviously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20carriers%20are%20lobbying%20against%20the%20bill%20through%20trade%20association%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airlines.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirlines%20for%20America%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20has%20made%20opposition%20against%20the%20bill%20one%20of%20its%20key%20focuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-cards-congress-competition-act-rewards-wipe-out-southwest-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%20to%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Southwest%20Airlines%20said%20the%20bill%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20policy%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20%26quot%3Bundermine%2C%20if%20not%20completely%20end%2C%20credit%20card%20rewards%20programs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSouthwest%20strongly%20opposes%20the%20CCCA%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20asked%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20bill%2C%20an%20American%20Airlines%20spokesperson%20also%20said%20the%20Act%20would%20%26quot%3Bseverely%20restrict%26quot%3B%20loyalty%20rewards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNearly%2030%20million%20Americans%20nationwide%20hold%20an%20airline%20credit%20card%2C%20and%20this%20legislation%20would%20destroy%20cardmembers'%20ability%20to%20earn%20rewards%2C%20miles%2C%20and%20the%20myriad%20benefits%20that%20go%20along%20with%20cobranded%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20Airlines%20CEO%20Scott%20Kirby%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcongress-billcredit-card-fees-kill-flier-miles-united-scott-kirby-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriticized%20the%20bill%20in%20an%20earnings%20call%20on%20October%2018%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20warning%20that%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Bkill%26quot%3B%20rewards%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B84%25%20of%20US%20consumers%20have%20some%20kind%20of%20rewards%20card%20in%20their%20wallet.%20I%20bet%20almost%20everyone%20in%20this%20call%20has%20one%2C%20and%20they%20like%20them%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.united.com%2Fevents%2Fevent-details%2F3q23-earnings-call%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BOur%20customers%20certainly%20like%20them%20a%20lot.%20And%20so%20I%20think%20it'd%20be%20hard%20in%20Congress%20to%20take%20a%20vote%20that%2084%25%20of%20your%20voters%20are%20going%20to%20be%20upset%20with%20the%20outcome%20of%20that%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20losing%20credit%20card%20rewards%20programs%20could%20create%20troubles%20for%20airlines%20that%20go%20beyond%20irate%20customers%20missing%20their%20free%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarriers%20typically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Faerospace-defense%2Fus-airline-loyalty-programs-can-provide-buffer-possible-recession-2023-04-04%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearn%20billions%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20partnering%20with%20credit%20card%20companies%20to%20issue%20co-branded%20cards.%20These%20cards%20give%20rewards%20like%20miles%20to%20consumers%20on%20every%20spend%20%E2%80%94%20and%20pay%20the%20airlines%20each