ests%20it%20has%20communal%20overtones%20and%20that%20the%20gathering%20will%20take%20place%20in%20the%20Old%20Delhi%20area%2C%20which%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20a%20communally%20sensitive%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20group%20called%20%E2%80%98Mission%20Save%20Constitution%E2%80%99%20is%20behind%20the%20now-cancelled%20event.%20Although%20permission%20for%20the%20gathering%20was%20granted%20earlier%20by%20both%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%2C%20it%20was%20later%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20upheld%20the%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20permission.%20In%20its%20order%2C%20the%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fdelhi-high-court-forbids-all-india-muslim-mahapanchayat-ramlila-maidan%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CBetween%20Navratri%20and%20Diwali%2C%20there%20are%20several%20festivals%20like%20Karvachauth%2C%20Dhanteras%2C%20etc.%20The%20period%20from%20the%20end%20of%20Shraddh%20to%20Diwali%20is%20extremely%20auspicious%20for%20the%20Hindu%20community.%20Though%20the%20event%20has%20been%20styled%20as%20a%20purpose%20for%20educating%20the%20people%20about%20their%20rights%2C%20the%20tenor%20of%20the%20posters%20indicates%20that%20they%20can%20have%20communal%20overtones%20which%20can%20result%20in%20an%20increase%20in%20communal%20tensions%20in%20the%20Old%20Delhi%20area%20which%20is%20a%20sensitive%20area%20as%20people%20from%20different%20communities%20live%20there%20and%20the%20communal%20violence%20in%20the%20area%20is%20not%20unknown.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20petitioner%20organisation%20can%20hold%20its%20event%20after%20the%20festivals%20are%20over%20and%20can%20approach%20the%20authorities%20afresh%20for%20permission.%20It%20told%20the%20authorities%20that%20they%20could%20take%20a%20call%20regarding%20permission%20depending%20upon%20the%20merits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMission%20Save%20Constitution%20has%20advocate%20Mehmood%20Pracha%20as%20its%20national%20convener%3B%20Wajahat%20Habibullah%2C%20former%20chairperson%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Minorities%2C%20as%20its%20principal%20advisor%3B%20Justice%20B.G.%20Kolse%2C%20former%20high%20court%20judge%2C%20as%20its%20advisor%3B%20and%20Islamic%20cleric%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20Raza%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698302835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F29142658%2F5606166528_b12b9c251a_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-denies-permission-for-muslim-mahapanchayat-says-event-may-spark-communal-tensions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Subramonium%20Prasad%20said%20permission%20cannot%20be%20granted%20for%20the%20October%2029%20event%20in%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20in%20Delhi%20as%20there%20are%20several%20Hindu%20festivals%20around%20that%20time.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-denies-permission-for-muslim-mahapanchayat-says-event-may-spark-communal-tensions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Robert%20Card%2C%20Main%20Suspect%20In%20US%20Shooting%20That%20Killed%2022%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20emergency%20alert%20has%20been%20sounded%20in%20a%20county%20in%20US'%20Maine%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F10-killed-many-injured-in-shootings-at-maine-in-us-gunman-not-caught-yet-news-agency-afp-quoting-us-media-4514404%5C%22%3E22%20people%20were%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20dozens%20injured%20in%20shootings.%20Police%20have%20launched%20a%20massive%20operation%20to%20catch%20the%20gunman%2C%20who%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Robert%20Card%2C%20and%20asked%20locals%20in%20Lewiston%20to%20stay%20inside%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20active%20shooter%20in%20Lewiston.%20We%20ask%20p