atimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fgoogle-is-making-more-money-than-it-did-in-the-last-12-months%2Farticleshow%2F104717762.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Disney's%20Sales%20To%20Reliance%20Will%20Follow%20Rupert%20Murdoch's%20Logic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20new%20class%20of%20competition%20is%20disrupting%20legacy%20media%20in%20the%20world's%20most-populous%20nation%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20second%20change%20in%20the%20ownership%20of%20a%20popular%20franchise%20in%20four%20years.%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20was%20the%20first%20to%20see%20the%20threat.%20Now%20it's%20Bob%20Iger's%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Walt%20Disney%20Co.%20boss%20is%20nearing%20a%20multi-billion-dollar%20deal%20to%20sell%20his%20Indian%20operations%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20reported%20this%20week.%20In%202019%2C%20Iger%20was%20the%20buyer%2C%20and%20Murdoch%20the%20seller.%20The%20Star%20India%20business%20came%20to%20Disney%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%2471%20billion%20global%20acquisition%20of%2021st%20Century%20Fox%20Inc.'s%20entertainment%20assets.%20Even%20that%20transaction%20had%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMurdoch%20received%20a%20warning%20shot%20when%20an%20upstart%20%E2%80%94%20Facebook%20Inc.%20%E2%80%94%20turned%20up%20at%20a%202017%20Indian%20cricket%20league%20auction%20with%20a%20%24600%20million%20bid%20for%20streaming%20rights.%20Star%20saw%20off%20the%20threat%20by%20paying%20%242.55%20billion%20for%20television%20and%20web%20for%20five%20years%2C%20but%20the%20writing%20was%20on%20the%20wall%20%E2%80%94%20the%20internet%20was%20coming%20for%20sports%20programming%2C%20the%20crown%20jewel%20of%20appointment%20viewing.%20Three%20months%20later%2C%20the%20Australian-born%20media%20mogul%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20Iger.%20The%20transaction%20closed%20after%20about%2015%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20challenger%20is%20not%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20but%20Mukesh%20Ambani.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20Indian%20tycoon's%20fledgling%204G%20telco%20was%20just%20starting%20to%20disrupt%20the%20wireless%20industry%20with%20free%20voice%20calls%20and%20cheap%20data.%20Six%20years%20later%2C%20he%20has%20more%20than%20400%20million%20customers%2C%20and%20a%20burgeoning%20consumer%20empire%20blurring%20the%20lines%20between%20carriage%2C%20content%20and%20commerce.%20The%20country's%20digital%20market%20has%20exploded%2C%20but%20has%20also%20effectively%20shrunk%20into%20a%20duopoly.%20Legacy%20TV%20doesn't%20stand%20a%20chance%20for%20too%20long%20in%20this%20altered%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20why%20Iger%20is%20offloading%20the%20business%20in%20his%20second%20stint%20as%20the%20Disney%20chief%20executive.%20He's%20valuing%20Star%20India%20%E2%80%94%20or%20Disney%20Star%20as%20it%20is%20now%20called%20%E2%80%94%20at%20%2410%20billion.%20Ambani%20views%20the%20assets%20at%20between%20%247%20billion%20and%20%248%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg%20News.%20A%20successful%20transaction%20will%20be%20a%20demonstration%20of%20Iger's%20promise%20to%20take%20the%20behemoth%20closer%20to%20its%20core%20offerings%20of%20theme%20parks%2C%20Hulu%20and%20Disney%2B%2C%20and%20ESPN.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Ambani%2C%20too%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20critical%20validation.%20Foreign%20participation%20in%20Indian%20TV%20began%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20with%20a%20satellite%20transponder%20leased%20from%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20billionaire%20Li%20Ka-shing.%20Murdoch%20entered%20in%201993%20by%20buying%20Star%20from%20Li.%20Things%20are%20going%20to%20be%20different%20now.%20Japan's%20Sony%20Group%20Corp.%20will%20still%20be%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20television%20network%20once%20it%20closes%20its%20long-pending%20merger%20with%20the%20homegrown%20Zee%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%20Ltd.%20But%20Ambani%20will%20likely%20control%20a%20bigger%20share%20of%20consumers'%20wallets%20and%20advertisers'%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20a%20deal%20with%20Iger%20will%20help%20bring%20credibility%20to%20three%20of%20Ambani's%20propositions%20%E2%80%94%20digital%2C%20retail%20and%20consumer%20finance.%20Last%20year%2C%20Ambani%20wrote%20a%20%242.7%20billion%20check%20and%20snagged%20the%20streaming%20rights%20for%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20from%20Disney%2C%20essentially%20succeeding%20where%20Zuckerberg%20had%20failed%20in%202017.%20He%20also%20poached%20some%20of%20the%20key%20executives%20that%20had%20helped%20make%20Star%20India%2C%20and%20especially%20its%20Hotstar%20streaming%20service%2C%20a%20valuable%20franchise%20for%20Murdoch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Disney%2B%20Hotstar%20platform%20in%20India%20is%20currently%20riding%20the%20wave%20of%20record%20World%20Cup%20Cricket%20viewership%2C%20the%20momentum%20has%20shifted%20toward%20Ambani's%20JioCinema.%20All%20he%20needs%20to%20do%20now%20is%20to%20translate%20some%20of%20those%20eyeballs%20into%20consumer%20spending%20%E2%80%94%20both%20in%20his%20own%20stores%20and%20at%20the%20mom-and-pop%20shops%20affiliated%20with%20his%20retail%20network%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20will%20have%20a%20story%20for%20investors.%20Brands%20that%20wants%20to%20sell%20nationally%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20succeed%20unless%20they%20go%20through%20Ambani%2C%20in%20media%20as%20well%20as%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20some%20of%20these%20brands%20%E2%80%94%20from%20cheap%20smartphones%20and%20laptops%20to%20fuzzy%20drinks%20and%20food%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20Ambani's%20own.%20He%20will%20get%20to%20advertise%20them%20practically%20for%20free%20and%20drive%20demand%20with%20cheap%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJio%2C%20together%20with%20other%20Indian%20carriers%2C%20is%20also%20lobbying%20the%20telecom%20regulator%20for%20a%20right%20to%20charge%20large%20internet-traffic%20generators%2C%20such%20as%20Netflix%20Inc.%2C%20a%20network-usage%20fee.%20That%20controversial%20levy%20will%20put%20pure-play%20content%20companies%20at%20a%20disadvantage%20to%20Ambani's%20dominance%20across%20multiple%2C%20interconnected%20markets.%20(In%20August%2C%20Netflix%20decided%20to%20bundle%20its%20offering%20with%20Jio's%20mobile%20data%20plans.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20the%20only%20serious%20competition%20the%20conglomerate%20may%20face%20is%20from%20Amazon.com%20Inc.%20and%20the%20Mumbai-based%20Tata%20Group.%20Neither%20of%20them%20owns%20a%20telco%2C%20and%20Tata%20Group%20is%20absent%20from%20media%2C%20but%20at%20least%20they%20will%20compete%20against%20Ambani%20in%20three%20out%20of%20the%20five%20areas%3A%C2%A0%20wireless%2C%20on-screen%20entertainment%2C%20physical%20retail%2C%20e-commerce%20and%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20the%20mature%20US%20market%2C%20cable%20will%20eventually%20succumb%20to%20cord-cutting%20in%20India%2C%20too.%20But%20traditional%20TV%20still%20has%20a%20huge%20following%20among%20the%20nation's%201.4%20billion%20people.%20The%20real%20problem%20lies%20elsewhere.%20A%20media%20titan%20with%20a%20weakening%20grasp%20on%20cricket%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20much%20of%20a%20chance%20to%20make%20Bollywood%20work%20in%20its%20favor%20%E2%80%94%20doesn't%20have%20a%20third%20magic%20bullet%20in%20India.%20Before%20buying%2021st%20Century%20Fox%2C%20Disney%20had%20acquired%20a%20local%20studio%20to%20produce%20Hindi-language%20movies.%20That%20dream%20soured%20in%20about%20four%20years.%20By%20contrast%2C%20the%20Star%20Studios%20setup%20it%20got%20later%20from%20Murdoch%20is%20successful%2C%20but%20there%20may%20not%20be%20any%20point%20in%20holding%20on%20to%20it%20if%20Indian%20creators%20don't%20allow%20it%20to%20profit%20off%20their%20intellectual%20property.%20The%20World%20Cup%20cricket%20rights%20will%20expire%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIger%20would%20be%20wise%20to%20follow%20Murdoch's%20lead%20and%20cash%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Andy%20Mukherjee%20is%20a%20Bloomberg%20Opinion%20columnist%20covering%20industrial%20companies%20and%20financial%20services.%20He%20previously%20was%20a%20columnist%20for%20Reuters%20Breakingviews.%20He%20has%20also%20worked%20for%20the%20Straits%20Times%2C%20ET%20NOW%20and%20Bloomberg%20News.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698299460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2F91g533e4_mukesh-ambani-pti-650_625x300_28_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdisneys-sales-to-reliance-will-follow-rupert-murdochs-logic-4514872%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20class%20of%20competition%20is%20disrupting%20legacy%20media%20in%20the%20world's%20most-populous%20nation%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20second%20change%20in%20the%20ownership%20of%20a%20popular%20franchise%20in%20four%20years.%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20was%20the%20first%20to%20see%20the%20threat.%20Now%20it's%20Bob%20Iger's%20turn.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdisneys-sales-to-reliance-will-follow-rupert-murdochs-logic-4514872%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdisneys-sales-to-reliance-will-follow-rupert-murdochs-logic-4514872%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdisneys-sales-to-reliance-will-follow-rupert-murdochs-logic-4514872%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Double%20tap%20on%20Apple%20Watch%3A%20How%20Apple%20implemented%20its%20'coolest'%20feature%20of%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698299457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104717496%2Cimgsize-874260.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fdouble-tap-on-apple-watch-how-apple-implemented-its-coolest-feature-of-2023%2Farticleshow%2F104717496.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20has%20introduced%20a%20new%20double%20tap%20gesture%20for%20its%20Watch%20Series%209%20and%20Watch%20Ultra%202%20models.%20The%20feature%20allows%20users%20to%20perform%20common%20actions%20by%20tapping%20their%20index%20finger%20and%20thumb%20together%20twice.%20While%20the%20gesture%20looks%20cool%2C%20there%20is%20some%20skepticism%20about%20its%20reliability.%20Apple%20claims%20to%20have%20ensured%20that%20the%20gesture%20is%20triggered%20accurately%20by%20using%20an%20algorithm%20that%20detects%20wrist%20movements%20and%20changes%20in%20blood%20flow.%20However%2C%20the%20double%20tap%20feature%20is%20currently%20limited%20and%20does%20not%20work%20underwater%20or%20in%20certain%20apps%20and%20features.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AABHAS%20SHARMA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fdouble-tap-on-apple-watch-how-apple-implemented-its-coolest-feature-of-2023%2Farticleshow%2F104717496.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australia%20returns%20smuggled%20historical%20artefacts%20to%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698299451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F14E13%2Fproduction%2F_131532558_tang-dynasty-polychrome-horse-and-rider-839x410-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67224568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20dinosaur%20fossil%20and%20two%20Tang%20Dynasty%20figurines%20were%20handed%20to%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20in%20Canberra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67224568%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67224568.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67224568.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Simultaneous%20Polls%20Only%20Possible%20by%202029%2C%20Law%20Commission%20Tells%20Kovind%20Panel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26110403%2FThe-Wire-56.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Law%20Commission%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2025%2C%20presented%20a%20roadmap%2C%20including%20possible%20changes%20required%20to%20the%20constitution%2C%C2%A0to%20the%20high-level%20panel%20headed%20by%20former%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20looking%20into%20the%20proposal%20of%20simultaneous%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Flaw-commission-presents-roadmap-on-one-nation-one-election-to-ram-nath-kovind-led-panel%2Farticle67459227.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%3Cem%3E%20The%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20commission%20said%20the%20proposal%20can%20only%20be%20materialised%20by%20the%202029%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20as%20it%20would%2C%20over%20time%2C%20work%20out%20a%20formula%20to%20synchronise%20all%20assembly%20elections%2C%20either%20by%20extending%20or%20reducing%20the%20tenures%20of%20respective%20state%20assemblies.%20A%20report%20from%20the%20Law%20Commission%20is%20still%20pending%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20invited%20again%20for%20another%20round%20of%20discussions%20by%20the%20Kovind%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Law%20Commission%20is%20looking%20into%20the%20proposal%20of%20holding%20assembly%20and%20parliament%20elections%20at%20once%2C%20the%20panel%20headed%20by%20the%20former%20president%20is%20exploring%20ways%20to%20synchronise%20assembly%2C%20parliament%2C%20municipality%2C%20and%20panchayat%20elections%20all%20at%20once.%20The%20Kovind%20Panel%20has%20been%20officially%20renamed%20as%20the%C2%A0High%20Level%20Committee%20(HLC)%20on%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%2C%20a%20Law%20Ministry%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20HLC%20has%20already%20written%20to%20political%20parties%20across%20the%20country%20to%20elicit%20their%20views%20on%20the%20matter.%20Letters%20have%20so%20far%20been%20sent%20to%20six%20national%20parties%2C%2033%20state%20parties%2C%20and%20seven%20registered%20unrecognised%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20Wednesday%E2%80%99s%20meeting%2C%20the%20HLC%20took%20%E2%80%9Cnote%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20resignation%20of%20the%C2%A0resignation%20of%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20from%20membership%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20former%20leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%3B%20law%20minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%3B%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%2015th%20finance%20commission%20N.K.%20Singh%3B%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%20Subhash%20C.%20Kashyap%3B%20senior%20advocate%20Harish%20Salve%3B%20and%20former%20chief%20vigilance%20commissioner%20Sanjay%20Kothari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20official%20notification%20issued%20on%20September%202%2C%20constituting%20the%20Kovind%20Panel%2C%20the%20government%20said%20holding%20frequent%20elections%20so%20far%20has%20resulted%20in%20massive%20expenditure%2C%20diversion%20of%20official%20machinery%20for%20election%20purposes%2C%20and%20disruption%20in%20developmental%20activity%20due%20to%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%20Therefore%2C%20if%20simultaneous%20polls%20are%20held%2C%20the%20government%20notification%20said%2C%20all%20three%20of%20them%20can%20be%20tackled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20have%20been%20several%20criticisms%20against%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20of%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20election.%20Writing%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20former%20election%20commissioner%20Ashok%20Lavasa%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsimultaneous-polls-a-point-by-point-rebuttal-of-the-govts-reasoning-by-former-ec-ashok-lavasa%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20more%20meaningful%20and%20substantive%20electoral%20reforms%20that%20need%20the%20urgent%20attention%20of%20Parliament.%20There%20are%20far%20more%20effective%20ways%20to%20bring%20about%20greater%20transparency%20in%20election-related%20expenditure%20than%20chasing%20the%20mechanical%20scheduling%20of%20elections.%20Yes%2C%20there%20might%20be%20a%20need%20to%20bring%20about%20more%20managerial%20efficiency%20in%20conducting%20elections%20but%20that%20might%20not%20need%20onerous%20constitutional%20amendments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELavasa%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20the%20reasons%20cited%20by%20the%20government%20in%20favour%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%E2%80%99%20are%20nothing%20more%20than%20%E2%80%9Cinstinctive%20surmise(s)%20that%20cannot%20form%20a%20sufficient%20basis%20for%20taking%20a%20decision%20that%20has%20significant%20implications%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698299410000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26110403%2FThe-Wire-56.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsimultaneous-polls-only-possible-by-2029-law-commission-tells-kovind-panel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Law%20Commission%20said%20the%20proposal%20can%20only%20be%20materialised%20by%20the%202029%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20as%20it%20would%2C%20over%20time%2C%20work%20out%20a%20formula%20to%20synchronise%20all%20assembly%20elections%2C%20either%20by%20extending%20or%20reducing%20the%20tenures%20of%20state%20assemblies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22htt