20lead%20actors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Neil%20Soans%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmovie-reviews%2Fkillers-of-the-flower-moon%2Fmovie-review%2F104717460.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Finds%20Itself%20Increasingly%20Alone%20As%20Fury%20Grows%20Over%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJordan's%20Queen%20Rania%20Al%20Abdullah%20was%20offered%20a%20chance%20to%20express%20horror%20at%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20killing%20and%20abduction%20of%20Israelis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20she%20feel%2C%20she%20was%20asked%20in%20a%20CNN%20interview%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20an%20Arab%2C%20as%20a%20Palestinian%2C%20a%20human%20being%2C%20a%20mother%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20monarch%20launched%20into%20an%20impassioned%20denunciation%20of%20Israel's%20subsequent%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West's%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20standard%2C%26quot%3B%20juxtaposing%20what%20happened%20in%20southern%20Israel%20with%20what%20is%20occurring%20in%20Gaza.%20%26quot%3BAre%20we%20being%20told%20it%20is%20wrong%20to%20kill%20an%20entire%20family%20at%20gunpoint%20but%20it's%20OK%20to%20shell%20them%20to%20death%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%2C%20greeted%20with%20fury%20in%20Israel%2C%20is%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20disconnect%20between%20how%20the%20Jewish%20state%20views%20the%20conflict%2C%20and%20how%20it%20is%20seen%20by%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20many%20further%20afield.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInside%20Israel%2C%20a%20powerful%20sense%20of%20foreboding%20was%20evidenced%20by%20a%20new%20poll%20showing%2064%25%20of%20Israelis%20now%20fear%20for%20their%20physical%20safety.%20Hamas%20continues%20to%20fire%20rockets%20and%20missiles%20into%20the%20country%20every%20day%20while%20militants%20try%20to%20sneak%20in%20via%20land%20or%20sea.%20Security%20officials%20believe%20some%20of%20those%20who%20entered%20on%20October%207%20may%20be%20in%20hiding%20in%20preparation%20for%20a%20second%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20Israel%2C%20many%20see%20things%20differently.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20United%20Nations%20Secretary%20General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20said%20of%20the%20Hamas%20killings%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20happen%20in%20a%20vacuum%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Palestinian%20people%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%2056%20years%20of%20suffocating%20occupation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20ambassador%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20Gilad%20Erdan%2C%20was%20so%20outraged%20at%20the%20notion%20that%20Hamas'%20violence%20needed%20this%20context%20that%20he%20called%20on%20Guterres%20to%20resign.%20The%20sentiment%20wasn't%20limited%20to%20those%20on%20the%20right%20of%20Israeli%20politics.%20%26quot%3BDark%20are%20the%20days%20when%20the%20United%20Nations%20Secretary%20General%20condones%20terror%2C%26quot%3B%20opposition%20leader%20Benny%20Gantz%20posted%20to%20X%2C%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGermany%2C%20which%20has%20been%20quick%20to%20show%20its%20support%20to%20Israel%20in%20the%20days%20since%20the%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20made%20a%20point%20of%20rejecting%20its%20ally's%20demand.%20%26quot%3BThe%20UN%20secretary%20general%20has%20of%20course%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20German%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20government%20spokesman%20Steffen%20Hebestreit%20in%20Berlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraelis%20don't%20deny%20that%20the%20events%20of%20October%207%20-%20when%201%2C400%20were%20killed%20and%20another%20200%20people%20abducted%20-%20require%20context.%20But%20for%20them%2C%20that%20context%20is%20not%20the%20mistreatment%20of%20Palestinians.%20They%20see%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20as%20an%20extension%20of%20anti-Semitic%20assaults%20through%20the%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Holocaust%20memorial%20centre%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20known%20as%20Yad%20Vashem%2C%20issued%20a%20statement%20in%20response%20to%20Guterres%2C%20saying%20October%207%20was%20different%20from%20the%20Holocaust%20only%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20Jews%20have%20today%20a%20state%20and%20an%20army.%20We%20are%20not%20defenseless%20and%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20others.%20However%2C%20it%20puts%20to%20test%20the%20sincerity%20of%20world%20leaders%2C%20intellectuals%20and%20influencers%20who%20come%20to%20Yad%20Vashem%20and%20pledge%20'Never%20Again.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20parade%20of%20Western%20leaders%20through%20Tel%20Aviv%20offering%20solidarity%20and%20support.%20This%20follows%20a%20visit%20by%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20who%20came%20offering%20billions%20in%20military%20aid%20and%20referred%20to%20painful%20Jewish%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20visit%2C%20Israelis%20felt%20understood.%20They%20believed%20that%20their%20plan%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20would%20gain%20world%20sympathy%20as%20they%20publicized%20gruesome%20videos%20the%20killers%20themselves%20took%20of%20slaughter%20and%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Israeli%20fighter%20jets%20took%20to%20the%20skies%20over%20Gaza%20and%20bombarded%20it%2C%20killing%20thousands%2C%20that%20sympathy%20has%20come%20with%20qualifications%20they%20did%20not%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETurkey's%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20on%20Wednesday%20cancelled%20a%20visit%20to%20Israel%20that%20was%20meant%20to%20take%20place%20later%20this%20year%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BHamas%20isn't%20a%20terror%20organization%20but%20is%20instead%20a%20group%20of%20liberators%20and%20mujahideen%20defending%20their%20land%20and%20people.%20We%20will%20never%20allow%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20children.%26quot%3B%20Turkey%20also%20paused%20plans%20for%20energy%20cooperation%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElsewhere%20in%20the%20Muslim%20world%2C%20Malaysia's%20Prime%20Minister%20Anwar%20Ibrahim%20said%20that%20no%20Muslim%20leader%20expects%20the%20events%20in%20Gaza%20to%20be%20resolved%20easily.%20Why%3F%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20has%20become%20too%20arrogant%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20level%20of%20insanity%20to%20allow%20people%20to%20be%20butchered%2C%20babies%20to%20be%20killed%2C%20hospitals%20to%20be%20bombed%2C%20and%20schools%20to%20be%20destroyed.%20It%20is%20the%20height%20of%20barbarism%20in%20this%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20refers%20to%20Hamas%20as%20the%20new%20ISIS%2C%20and%20has%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20the%20militant%20group%2C%20which%20is%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSaying%20that%20Hamas%20is%20the%20new%20ISIS%20is%20not%20only%20analytically%20inaccurate%20but%20also%20carries%20the%20risk%20of%20making%20all%20residents%20of%20Gaza%20vulnerable%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lina%20Khatib%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20SOAS%20Middle%20East%20Institute%20in%20London.%20%26quot%3BArabs%20and%20Muslims%20are%20widely%20rejecting%20this%20simplistic%20and%20dangerous%20characterization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20world%20leaders%20are%20calling%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20that%20would%20allow%20for%20more%20aid%20to%20get%20into%20Gaza%2C%20although%20some%20describe%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhumanitarian%20pause.%26quot%3B%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20eight%20trucks%20got%20in%2C%20followed%20by%20another%2017%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20who%20said%20every%20truck%20was%20checked%20by%20their%20officers%20to%20make%20sure%20nothing%20was%20going%20in%20to%20help%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20aid%20that's%20arrived%20so%20far%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20drop%20in%20the%20ocean%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tommaso%20Della%20Longa%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20The%20International%20Federation%20of%20Red%20Cross%20and%20Red%20Crescent%20Societies%2C%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20as%20concerns%20grow%20that%20Hezbollah%20may%20enter%20the%20war%20from%20Lebanon%20to%20its%20north%2C%20some%20speak%20of%20leaving%20for%20the%20US%20or%20Europe%2C%20at%20least%20for%20a%20period.%20But%20others%20say%20the%20anti-Israeli%20demonstrations%20across%20Western%20cities%20make%20them%20feel%20even%20less%20safe%20abroad%20than%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20fight%2C%20many%20say%2C%20for%20the%20Jewish%20homeland%2C%20a%20second%20war%20of%20independence.%20But%20what%20that%20will%20create%20internally%20remains%20unclear.%20Gun%20license%20applications%2C%20officials%20report%2C%20are%20poised%20to%20triple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERachel%20Goldberg-Polin%2C%20whose%20son%20Hersh%20was%20taken%20captive%20by%20Hamas%20at%20a%20music%20festival%2C%20spoke%20at%20the%20UN%20and%20asked%20why%20there%20wasn't%20more%20agitation%20over%20the%20abducted.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20is%20the%20world%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20anguish.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20are%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698299100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fqhu2q2sg_gaza_625x300_26_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-finds-itself-increasingly-alone-as-fury-grows-over-gaza-4514438%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jordan's%20Queen%20Rania%20Al%20Abdullah%20was%20offered%20a%20chance%20to%20express%20horror%20at%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20killing%20and%20abduction%20of%20Israelis.%20How%20did%20she%20feel%2C%20she%20was%20asked%20in%20a%20CNN%20interview%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20an%20Arab%2C%20as%20a%20Palestinian%2C%20a%20human%20being%2C%20a%20mother%3F%26quot%3B%2