%3Cp%3EManuel%20Ballivian%20Figueroa%2FCatholic%20University%20of%20Santa%20Maria%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EResearchers%20recreated%20the%20face%20of%20an%20Inca%20girl%20who%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20sacrificed%20atop%20a%20volcano%20more%20than%20500%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Inca%20Ice%20Maiden%20is%20Peru's%20most%20famous%20mummy%2C%20discovered%20in%201995%20almost%20completely%20preserved.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20team%20of%20scientists%20worked%20with%20a%20Swedish%20sculptor%20to%20recreate%20her%20likeness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EArcheologists%20have%20recreated%20the%20possible%20face%20of%20Peru's%20famous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Farchaeologists-discover-mummy-peru-long-hair-ancient-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emummy%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20teenage%20girl%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20sacrificed%20in%20an%20Inca%20ritual%20to%20the%20gods%20more%20than%20500%20years%20ago%20in%20the%20Andes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20her%20discovery%20in%201995%20near%20the%20summit%20of%20the%20Ampato%20volcano%2C%20the%20girl%20has%20come%20to%20be%20known%20by%20several%20nicknames%20including%20The%20Lady%20of%20Ampato%2C%20The%20Inca%20Ice%20Maiden%20%E2%80%94%20because%20of%20the%20frozen%20conditions%20atop%20the%20mountain%20that%20allowed%20her%20body%20to%20remain%20preserved%20for%20hundreds%20of%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20simply%2C%20Juanita.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohan%20Reinhard%2C%20a%20US%20anthropologist%2C%20and%20his%20climbing%20partner%20Miguel%20Z%C3%A1rate%20stumbled%20upon%20Juanita%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20feet%20atop%20the%20towering%20volcano%20located%20in%20the%20Andes%20of%20southern%20Peru%20during%20an%20expedition%20nearly%20three%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I'd%20never%20know%20what%20her%20face%20looked%20like%20when%20she%20was%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20Reinhard%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fperu-mummy-face-reconstruction-3052c25426b5393dc93fa36861516b63%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Associated%20Press.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20researchers%20unveiled%20the%20recreation%20of%20Juanita's%20head%20and%20torso%20alongside%20three-dimensional%20scans%20of%20her%20mummy%20in%20a%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Andean%20Sanctuaries%20Museum%20of%20the%20Catholic%20University%20of%20Santa%20Maria%20in%20Arequipa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20Polish%20and%20Peruvian%20scientists%20worked%20with%20a%20Swedish%20sculptor%20experienced%20in%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20ancient%20faces%20to%20create%20the%20modern%20restoration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOscar%20Nilsson%2C%20the%20Swedish%20archeologist%20and%20sculptor%2C%20told%20The%20AP%20he%20spent%20about%20400%20hours%20of%20work%20on%20modeling%20Juanita's%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finca-child-sacrifice-ayahuasca-used-as-antidepressant-peru-mummies-show-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDagmara%20Socha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Polish%20bioarchaeologist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Warsaw's%20Center%20for%20Andean%20Studies%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20researchers%20first%20had%20to%20obtain%20a%20replica%20of%20Juanita's%20skull.%20Next%2C%20researchers%20working%20on%20the%20project%20completed%20body%20scans%20on%20her%20mummified%20body%2C%20conducted%20DNA%20studies%2C%20and%20compiled%20her%20ethnological%20characteristics%2C%20including%20age%20and%20complexion%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported%2C%20citing%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropological%20studies%20put%20Juanita's%20likely%20age%20between%2013%20and%2015%20years%20old%20when%20she%20died%20sometime%20between%201440%20and%201450%20AD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%20performed%20a%20CT%20scan%20and%20determined%20she%20was%20most%20likely%20killed%20by%20