https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-says-he-will-have-to-answer-for-what-happened-on-7-october-in-address-to-the-nation-12992577%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20Commission%20Gets%20Memorandums%20From%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20Over%20%E2%80%98Poll%20Violations%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25220532%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-10.04.47%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20only%20weeks%20to%20go%20for%20assembly%20elections%20in%20five%20states%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Congress%20knocked%20on%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%E2%80%99s%20door%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2025%2C%20alleging%20poll%20code%20violations%20by%20each%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Wednesday%20afternoon%2C%20a%20BJP%20delegation%20including%20Union%20ministers%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20and%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%2C%20MP%20Radha%20Mohan%20Das%20Agarwal%2C%20and%20party%20leaders%20Anil%20Baluni%20and%20Om%20Pathak%20went%20to%20the%20EC%20office%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20demanding%20legal%20action%20against%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20memorandum%20says%20that%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20at%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Dausa%2C%20Rajasthan%20on%20October%2020%20said%20that%20she%20saw%20on%20television%20that%20an%20envelope%20carrying%20a%20donation%20made%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20Devnarayan%20Temple%20contained%20Rs%2021.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20said%20that%20she%20saw%20it%20on%20television%20and%20could%20not%20say%20whether%20it%20was%20true%20or%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20compared%20the%20alleged%20donation%20to%20other%20developments%20in%20the%20country%2C%20claiming%20that%20while%20several%20declarations%20are%20made%20on%20stage%20during%20elections%2C%20all%20such%20promises%20are%20later%20found%20to%20be%20%3Cem%3Ejumlas%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20statement%20of%20Smt.%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20has%20violated%20the%20very%20basic%20foundation%20of%20free%20%26amp%3B%20fair%20elections%20by%20invoking%20the%20personal%20religious%20devotion%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BJP%20memorandum%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20memorandum%20said%20that%20with%20her%20speech%2C%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20had%20violated%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20the%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20added%20that%20Modi%20had%20visited%20the%20temple%20in%20Bhilwara%20in%20January%2C%20more%20than%20eight%20months%20before%20the%20declaration%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20quantum%20of%20his%20offerings%20are%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20public%20debate%20or%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20elections.%20To%20mock%20an%20individual%20for%20his%20devotion%20and%20faith%20on%20any%20basis%20whatsoever%20amounts%20to%20public%20abuse%2C%20denigration%20and%20vilification%20of%20the%20individual%2C%20the%20religion%20and%20its%20followers%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeven%20Congress%20complaints%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20couple%20of%20hours%20later%2C%20a%20delegation%20of%20the%20Congress%20reached%20the%20EC%20office%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20with%20seven%20charges%20against%20BJP%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20delegation%20included%20MPs%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20former%20union%20minister%20Salman%20Khurshid%2C%20and%20leaders%20Manikrao%20Thakre%2C%20and%20Mallu%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20complaint%20was%20against%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20election%20speech%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Rajnandgaon%20on%20October%2016%2C%20in%20which%20he%20accused%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20orchestrating%20the%20killing%20of%20Bhuneshwar%20Sahu%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fchhattisgarh-communal-clash-father-son-duo-hacked-to-death-murder-accused-yet-to-be-arrested-101681446694020.html%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Biranpur%20village%20in%20April.%20Sahu%E2%80%99s%20father%20Ishwar%20has%20been%20fielded%20as%20a%20candidate%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20demanded%20action%20against%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20for%20his%20speech%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20on%20October%2018%20for%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20cut%20intention%20to%20incite%20sections%20of%20society%20against%20one%20another.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20also%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20orders%20directing%20civil%20servants%20and%20Indian%20Army%20soldiers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%5C%22%3Epromote%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20sought%20the%20disqualification%20of%20Govind%20Singh%20Rajput%2C%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Surkhi%20in%20Sagar%20district%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20He%20allegedly%20claimed%20that%20he%20would%20pay%20Rs%2025%20lakhs%20to%20booth%20prabharis%20where%20more%20votes%20would%20be%20cast%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20sought%20the%20disbursement%20of%20benefits%20under%20schemes%20introduced%20by%20the%20Telangana%20State%20Government%20before%20the%20date%20of%20filing%20nominations%20(November%203)%20or%20after%20the%20polling%20of%20votes%20(November%2030).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20memorandum%20also%20included%20a%20complaint%20against%20unlawful%20transfers%20and%20posting%20of%20police%20officers%20in%20Telangana%2C%20who%20have%20been%20transferred%20without%20completing%20two%20and%20half%20years%20of%20their%20tenure%2C%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20EC%2C%20along%20with%20a%20complaint%20against%20allotment%20of%20election%20duty%20to%20specific%20officers%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20publicly%20support%20a%20specific%20political%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEC%20as%20%E2%80%98Impartial%20Referee%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20role%20as%20a%20referee%20has%20been%20under%20intense%20scrutiny%2C%20particularly%20since%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20when%20shortly%20after%20the%20polls%2C%20an%20election%20commissioner%2C%20Ashok%20Lavasa%2C%20who%20was%20next%20in%20line%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-commissioner-ashok-lavasa-known-for-dissent-in-ec-may-leave-early-for-adb-job%5C%22%3Eleft%20the%20EC%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20joined%20the%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%20in%20Manila%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20move.%20Incidentally%2C%20Lavasa%20was%20revealed%20to%20be%20the%20only%20person%20in%20the%20three-member%20commission%20who%20had%20voted%20against%20issuing%20clean%20chits%20to%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20for%20speeches%20that%20were%20contentious%20and%20which%20the%20opposition%20had%20complained%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%2C%20in%20the%20monsoon%20session%20in%20parliament%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnew-bill-selection-of-election-commissioners%5C%22