yself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENageshu%20longed%20to%20be%20near%20home%20and%20spent%20a%20few%20more%20years%20working%20at%20a%20Hyderabad%20shopping%20mall%20before%20finally%20returning%20to%20his%20hometown.%20In%202011%2C%20his%20brother%20informed%20him%20of%20a%20job%20opening%20in%20the%20Indian%20Railways%2C%20where%20he%20landed%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F241986%2Fladakh-siachen-glacier-indian-army-jawans-bravery-porter-stanzin-padma-jeevan-raksha-padak-award-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20as%20a%20porter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20years%20of%20struggle%2C%20when%20I%20was%20able%20to%20have%20a%20stable%20job%20as%20a%20porter%2C%20I%20was%20sure%20I%20wanted%20to%20help%20people%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20even%20while%20working%20and%20supporting%20his%20family%2C%20Nageshu%20kept%20putting%20money%20aside%20for%20his%20future.%20And%20in%202020%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20Nageshu%20was%20left%20without%20a%20job%20like%20most%20others.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20he%20noticed%20how%20most%20underprivileged%20children%20in%20his%20neighbourhood%20were%20dropping%20out%20of%20school.%20He%20decided%20to%20use%20his%20savings%20and%20start%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326708%2Fdattu-agarwal-free-residential-school-for-girls-with-visual-impairment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20coaching%20class%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20these%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20%E2%80%98Nageshu%20Sir%E2%80%99%20has%20taught%20hundreds%20of%20students%20from%20Classes%206%20to%2012%20for%20free.%20Currently%2C%20he%20teaches%20a%20batch%20of%2070%20students%20in%20his%20coaching%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20friends%20and%20family%20tell%20me%20how%20this%20coaching%20ce