0for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20an%20MS%20patient%20manage%20to%20do%20all%20this%3F%20Ask%20her%20and%20Sudha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20you%20need%20is%20courage%20and%20support%20from%20the%20family.%E2%80%9D%20She%20is%20immensely%20grateful%20to%20her%20husband%20who%20took%20such%20good%20care%20of%20her%20down%20the%20years%2C%20without%20a%20single%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20cancer%20a%20decade%20ago.%C2%A0%20The%20couple%20has%20no%20children.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20all%20that%20she%20has%20gone%20through%2C%20she%20has%20a%20ready%20smile%20for%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayashree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMamtha%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20taught%20us%20to%20delegate%20work%20and%20encouraged%20us%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98our%20camp%E2%80%99.%20We%20all%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20this%20endeavour%20of%20hers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20after%20almost%20three%20decades%2C%20some%20of%20the%20students%20share%20their%20fond%20memories%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20Manasa%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlways%20calm%20and%20composed%20with%20a%20smiling%20face%2C%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20was%20the%20calm%20within%20the%20storm%20of%20kids%20at%20Siddhi%20Creations.%20She%20embodies%20Maria%20Montessori%E2%80%99s%20(an%20Italian%20educator)%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98follow%20the%20child%E2%80%99.%20She%20gave%20us%20the%20freedom%20to%20create%20and%20thrive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajath%2C%20who%20is%20an%20advocate%20today%2C%20notes%20how%20%E2%80%9CSudha%20aunty%20showered%20the%20same%20love%20on%20all%20of%20us%20and%20took%20care%20of%20all%20details%2C%20giving%20us%20the%20lesson%20of%20what%20true%20leadership%20was.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20Vijetha%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20HR%20in%20an%20MNC%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20and%20the%20camps%20were%20%E2%80%9Can%20important%20part%20of%20my%20childhood%2C%20in%20framing%20our%20minds%20and%20adding%20value.%E2%80%9D%20Harshith%2C%20another%20student%20of%20the%20camp%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20green%20surroundings%2C%20the%20teachers%20and%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20with%20a%20happy%20face%20are%20unforgettable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20echoes%20these%20feelings%20when%20she%20says%20that%20it%20was%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20smile%20and%20happiness%20that%20was%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20satisfaction%20and%20contentment%20in%20running%20the%20camps%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%20octogenarian%20from%20her%20wheelchair.%C2%A0%20Her%20voice%20is%20now%20feeble%20but%20the%20spirit%20is%20as%20strong%20as%20ever.%20There%20is%20talk%20of%20reviving%20the%20camps%20among%20the%20teachers%20who%20are%20excited%20and%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAuthored%20by%20Jayalakshmi%20Menon.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20picture%20credits%20go%20to%20Sudha%20Iyengar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698072965000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20brainchild%20of%20Sudha%20Iyengar%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20was%20a%20venture%20to%20keep%20young%20children%20engaged%20fruitfully%20and%20joyfully%20during%20summer%20vacations%20while%20also%20picking%20up%20on%20essential%20life%20skills.%20With%20managing%20her%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20condition%2C%20Sudha's%20smile%20for%20everyone%20who%20enters%20her%20home%20has%20been%20winning%20hearts%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332837%2Fbengaluru-multiple-sclerosis-summer-camps-hobby-classes-sudha-iyengar-senior-citizen%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Doctor%20or%20a%20Standup%20Comedian%3F%20Dr%20Pal%20Manickam%20On%20Using%20Laughter%20As%20Medicine%20For%20Millions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHey%2C%20after%20this%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20know%20you%20inside%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Palaniappan%20Manickam%20tells%20his%20patient%20before%20doing%20an%20endoscopy%2C%20making%20the%20patient%20laugh.%20The%20gastroenterologist%2C%20based%20out%20of%20Sacramento%20in%20California%2C%20USA%2C%20uses%20humour%20to%20make%20patients%20feel%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUntil%202020%2C%20only%20his%20patients%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327134%2Fqueer-comedian-navin-noronha-on-navigating-comedy-circuit-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappreciated%20his%20humour%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20thanks%20to%20social%20media%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20laughing%20with%20him.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20his%20video%20on%20COVID-19%20went%20viral%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20a%20genre%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%98Medcom%E2%80%99%20(medical%20comedy).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20positive%20response%20to%20his%20initial%20video%20led%20the%20doctor%20to%20create%20many%20videos%2C%20which%20focus%20on%20important%20medical%20topics%2C%20infused%20with%20humour%20to%20make%20them%20more%20palatable.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20around%20two%20million%20subscribers%20across%20YouTube%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20come%20to%20a%20gastroenterologist%20with%20diseases%20like%20haemorrhoids%20and%20piles%2C%20which%20they%20find%20embarrassing%20to%20describe.%20When%20patients%20have%20to%20discuss%20stool%20habits%2C%20related%20changes%2C%20acidity%20etc%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20open%20up%20right%20away.%20So%20I%20started%20breaking%20the%20ice%20using%20a%20joke.%20They%20loved%20it%2C%20so%20I%20stuck%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Pal%2C%20as%20he%20is%20fondly%20called%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20appreciation%20for%20the%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20humour%20boosted%20his%20morale%20and%20opened%20up%20doors%20for%20him%20at%20a%20standup%20comedy%20club%20in%20Bay%20Area%2C%20California%2C%20called%20%E2%80%98Building%2018%E2%80%99.%20This%20kicked%20off%20the%2039-year-old%E2%80%99s%20stint%20as%20a%20comedian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20joined%20Building%2018%20in%20May%202020%20and%20learnt%20tips%20and%20tricks%20on%20how%20to%20write%20a%20script%2C%20how%20to%20deliver%20a%20punch%2C%20what%20is%20stand-up%20comedy%20and%20much%20more.%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20much%20more%20difficult%20than%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20first%20standup%20show%20at%20the%20club%2C%20Dr%20Pal%20describes%20the%20experience%20as%20%E2%80%9Cincomparable%E2%80%9D.%20He%20says%20he%20spent%20hours%20preparing%20for%20his%2010-minute%20set%2C%20where%20he%20spoke%20about%20many%20serious%20medical%20issues%20in%20a%20comical%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20grab%20this%20chance%20that%20life%20had%20given%20him%2C%20the%20doctor%20dove%20head%20first%20into%20comedy%2C%20creating%20reels%20and%20videos%2C%20and%20doing%20shows.%20Today%2C%20he%20does%20his%20%E2%80%98medcom%E2%80%99%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20in%20the%20US%2C%20India%2C%20Malaysia%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20punchline%20for%20a%20health%20tip%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5_1yhDaDZfA%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautop