rovided%20the%20rental%20costs%20of%20the%20expensive%20machines%20required%20for%20the%20job%20through%20its%20partnership%20with%20the%20A.T.E.%20Chandra%20foundation%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20while%20the%20locals%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20team%20worked%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20translated%20into%20results%20on%20the%20ground.%20Although%20her%20NGO%20had%20been%20set%20up%20many%20years%20ago%20with%20the%20purpose%20of%20focussing%20on%20animal%20care%2C%20it%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20primarily%20focussed%20on%20saving%20and%20improving%20human%20lives%20in%20a%20country%20prone%20to%20natural%20and%20manmade%20calamities%20where%20government%20intervention%20is%20often%20inadequate%20or%20even%20absent.%20Human%20beings%2C%20at%20some%20level%2C%20took%20precedence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nutanben%20and%20her%20team%20began%20working%20in%20around%20330-odd%20villages%20and%20%3Cem%3Etalukas%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20comprise%20the%20Jalna%20district%2C%20the%20situation%20was%20not%20much%20better%20than%20it%20was%20in%20Beed.%20Water%20was%20very%20scarce%2C%20most%20of%20the%20water%20bodies%20in%20the%20region%20were%20silted%20up%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288219%2Fafter-visiting-drought-prone-villages-23-yo-plants-3-lakh-trees-in-three-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebone%20dry%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20tankers%20were%20the%20only%20way%20of%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20started%20working%2C%20each%20%3Cem%3Etehsil%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%208%20in%20Jalna%20district%20%E2%80%94%20survived%20on%20250%20tankers%20per%20day.%20Farmers%20were%20barely%20producing%20anything%20since%20there%20was%20no%20water%20for%20farming%3B%20meeting%20the%20basic%20consumption%20needs%20was%20a%20struggle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20when%20the%20team%20arrived%20in%20the%20district%2C%20v