o%20abate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20rocket%20science%20to%20reach%20a%20quick%20answer-%20poor%20rainfall%20%3D%20failed%20crop%20season%20%3D%20farmer%20debt%20%3D%20farmer%20suicide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20they%20came%20across%20another%20NGO%20already%20working%20on%20the%20simple%20model%20they%20have%20since%20adopted-%20silt%20removal%20and%20rejuvenation%20of%20water%20bodies.%20Primary%20research%20done%20by%20them%20showed%20that%20there%20are%20many%20water%20bodies%20across%20the%20country%20that%20have%20over%20the%20years%20become%20defunct%20or%20unable%20to%20hold%20much%20water%20due%20to%20heavy%20silting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20groundwater%20too%20fails%20to%20get%20recharged%20as%20the%20silt%20prevents%20the%20rainwater%20from%20reaching%20the%20bottom.%20But%20if%20someone%20removed%20the%20silt%2C%20the%20water%20body%20could%20be%20rejuvenated%20and%20even%20better%20the%20silt%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20usually%20quite%20fertile%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20used%20by%20farmers%20on%20their%20land%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F268059%2Fmeena-pawar-nashik-farmer-earns-lakhs-grape-debt-farming-success-story-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimprove%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%202016%20to%202019%2C%20the%20A.T.E%20CF%2C%20along%20with%2022-odd%20partner%20organisations%2C%20worked%20extensively%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20rejuvenate%20over%202%2C700%20water%20bodies%2C%20impacting%20around%204%2C200%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20dampened%20their%20efforts%20but%20did%20not%20stop.%20In%202020%20and%202021%2C%20work%20continued%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Karnataka.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20work%20picked%20up%20pace%20once%20again%20and%20916%20water%20bodies%20were%20rejuvenated%20in%2018%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%2